       <td valign=top width=300>


        <font size=+2 face="Arial", "Helvetica"><strong>Party of one: Aggghhhh!</strong></font><br>

<font size=-1 face="Arial", "Helvetica">        

        By <a href="mailto:letters@news.com">
			CNET STAFF</a><BR>

        
        
	
	November 18, 1996, 5 a.m. PT

        </font>


       

        <p>

<font  face="Times">




       

       


Vermel made me do it, but I suspect that good-fer-nuthin' secretary of mine, Trixie Pixel, put him up to it. Diving off 60 foot tall towers isn't my usual style, but this is Comdex, and nothing is usual here.<p>
--Skinny DuBaud
