<h2>Literature</h2>

<h4>General</h4>

<ul>
    <li><h4><a href="literature/" target="_top">The Literary
        Scene</a> </h4>
    </li>
    <li><a href="print-on-demand/index-eng.htm">Books on Demand</a>
        - writers publish their own books on the Internet</li>
    <li><a href="islamabad/index.htm">The Islamabad Declaration</a></li>
    <li><a href="kurd/index.htm">Kurdish Library and
        Documentation Center</a></li>
    <li><a href="rhodes/index.htm" target="_top">Writers' and
        Translators' Centre of Rhodes</a> - on Rhodes</li>
    <li><a href="visby/build.htm" target="_top">The Baltic Centre
        for Writers and Translators</a> - in Visby <ul>
            <li><a href="visby/news/newsletters.htm"
                target="_top">Newsletters</a></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>

