<DOCHDR>
http://www.marebalticum.se:80/print-on-demand/index-eng.htm 194.198.228.141 19970124031156 text/html 6076
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 03:22:36 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
Accept-Ranges: bytes
Last-Modified: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 11:05:05 GMT
Content-Length: 5878
