<DOCHDR>
http://www.marebalticum.se:80/islamabad/index.htm 194.198.228.141 19970124031243 text/html 6330
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 03:22:58 GMT
