<h1 align=center>Kurdish Culture Network</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><font size=4><b>The Kurdish Library and Documentation Center</b> (Kutupxana &ucirc; Navenda 
Dokumentasyon&ecirc; ya Kurd) is established in Stockholm, February 1996. Beside 
the <i>Library</i> there is a <i>Documentation</i> <i>Center</i> and a <i>Databank</i> wich is under 
construction.</font> </p>
</blockquote>
