<h2><a name="THURSDAY"><i>THURSDAY</i></a><i> SEPTEMBER 26</i> </h2>

<p><font size="4"><strong><i>17.00</i></strong></font><i><br>
</i><em>Official inauguration ceremony in the Acropolis Open Air
Theatre of Rhodes (Music, welcoming address by the Mayor of
Rhodes Giorgos Giannopoulous and speech by the Bulgarian poet
Blaga Dimitrova and Katerine Stenou, Director of section for
intercultural exchange UNESCO) </em></p>

<p><font size="4"><em><strong>19.00</strong></em></font><br>
<em>Reception offered by the Municipality of Rhodes in the
medieval castle KASTELO and addresses by delegates<br>
followed by performance &#147;Apocalypse Trial&#147;, an
inter-disciplinary mystery-play with puppets, using all
techniques, actors, stilt-walkers, music, song, mime, dance with
elements from literary classics. Production: Marionetteatern of
Stockholm, Michael Meschke. Actors and musicians from Sweden,
Greece, France, Argentina and Finland.</em> </p>

