<h2><a name="FRIDAY"><i>FRIDAY</i></a><i> SEPTEMBER 27</i> </h2>

<p><i>One-day cruise to Symi at self cost, approximately 3.000
GRD per person with Poetry reading on board</i>.<em> Return at 16
o'clock.</em></p>

<hr>

<p align="center"><font size="4"><em><strong>&quot;People in a
Landscape&quot;</strong></em></font><em> <br>
Throughout the week an art exhibition by artist Andreas Gedin <br>
illustrating what happens to a poem by Tomas Transtrmer while
going through translations will be presented in the new
writers&#146; and translators&#146; centre on Laskou Street 10 A</em></p>

