<head>
<title>Baltic Centre for Writers and Translators</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body background="images/bakgr.gif" link="#800019" vlink="#4B4D4C">
<div align=center><center>
<table COLSPEC="L20 L20">
<tr><td><img src="images/OVCENTRU.GIF" align=bottom width=180 height=137></td><td><font size=7>B</font><font size=5>UILDING BRIDGES<br>
AND BREAKING BARRIERS</font></td></tr>
</table>
</center></div>
<p><img src="images/prick.gif" align=bottom width=20 height=20> <font size=5>The Baltic Centre for Writers and Translators is unique</font><br>
because it unites so many countries - Finland, Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania, Russia, Poland, 
Germany, Denmark, Norway and Sweden. The aim is to build bridges across the Baltic, to 
break down old barriers and provide the peace and quiet to work in an inspiring 
environment. We are to be a living meeting place and help to spread knowledge of the 
literatures of our countries and in future add to improved and more relaxed human relations.</p>
<p align=center><a href="present-eng.htm"><img src="images/more.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=140 height=59></a> <a href="future.htm"><img src="images/future.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=140 height=59></a> <a href="news/newsletters.htm"><img src="images/newsknapp.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=140 height=59></a></p>
<p align=center><a href="http://www.marebalticum.se/rhodes/wt-centre.htm"><img src="images/rhode.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=286 height=59></a></p>
<h5 align=center><a href="present-eng.htm">More information</a> | <a href="future.htm">Future Projects</a> | <a href="news/newsletters.htm">Newsletters and reports</a> | <a href="members.htm">Members</a></h5>
</body>

