<H1>Sibe<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
</H1>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<FONT SIZE=4>Rojhilat bi reng&ecirc; z&ecirc;r &ucirc; z&icirc;v
e<BR>
Kosret li ser mij&ecirc; ye, sifar&icirc; ye<BR>
<BR>
Duh ji berf&ecirc; s&icirc;stir b&ucirc; mij<BR>
&Icirc;ro xweliya &ecirc;gir e, risas&icirc; ye<BR>
<BR>
&Ccedil;ile ye, l&ecirc; wek demek ji bihar&ecirc;<BR>
Erd nerm e, hewa nerm e, sibeheke a&#136;sit&icirc; ye<BR>
<BR>
D&icirc;k bang dike, d&ucirc; bi ser kulekan ket<BR>
Li j&ecirc;r xule-xula av&ecirc;, &ccedil;avkan&icirc; ye<BR>
<BR>
&Ccedil;iv&icirc;k dixw&icirc;nin, l&ecirc; gol b&ecirc;deng e
<BR>
H&icirc;n di xewn&ecirc;n ^sev&ecirc; da ye, z&icirc;v&icirc;n&icirc;
ye<BR>
<BR>
Roj&ecirc; l&ecirc; da, pel&ecirc;n &#136;sevnem&icirc; di&ccedil;irisin
<BR>
Zev&icirc; &#136;s&icirc;n b&ucirc;ne, keskezer &ucirc; &ccedil;&icirc;man&icirc;
ye<BR>
<BR>
Bayek&icirc; sivik dil&icirc;ze bi pel&ecirc;n dara b&icirc;y&ecirc;
<BR>
Dem &ccedil;&ucirc;, &ecirc;d&icirc; zer&#136;s&icirc;n &ucirc;
&#136;serab&icirc; ye<BR>
<BR>
Duguhure dem bi dem, deqqe bi deqqe<BR>
Wek roj&ecirc;n pay&icirc;z&ecirc; ne, hery&ecirc;k y&ecirc;ke
d&icirc; ye<BR>
<BR>
Bin&ecirc;r nuha j&icirc; d&ucirc;maneke tozpembe<BR>
L&ecirc; ew j&icirc; &ccedil;&ucirc;, &ccedil;iya reng bi reng
in &ucirc; ezman binew&#136;s&icirc; ye<BR>
<BR>
<I>&Ccedil;iley&ecirc; P&ecirc;^s&icirc;n, 1994<BR>
<BR>
</I></FONT>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
