<H1>Pirsyar sebaret be awareyek<BR>
<BR>
</H1>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<FONT SIZE=4>Le j&icirc;lemoy wu&#136;sey dildar&icirc; w taset
da,<BR>
Le gulaw&icirc; henaset da<BR>
W&ecirc;ney telx&icirc; xom deb&icirc;nim.<BR>
Le giloley pe&#136;sokaw&icirc; gift &ucirc; got da<BR>
Perey dil&icirc; helkir&ucirc;zaw &ucirc; nakam&icirc; xom deb&icirc;nim.
<BR>
He&#136;sbestekanim le namey dildar&icirc;t da,<BR>
Zor car deng&icirc; naskoleyan d&ecirc;te ber g&ouml;m<BR>
Le xo&#136;siyan...<BR>
Le &#136;sepol&icirc; end&ecirc;&#136;sey q&ucirc;l&#180;a dexink&ecirc;m.
<BR>
Bo raburd&ucirc;y &#136;sermezar&icirc; xom deger&ecirc;m<BR>
B&icirc;tas&ecirc;nim,<BR>
B&icirc;fewt&ecirc;nim,<BR>
La&#136;sey kirmol&icirc; le &ccedil;aw&icirc;<BR>
Hem&ucirc; &#136;seydayek&icirc; rast &ucirc; bir&icirc;ndar da
<BR>
Wek&ucirc; n&icirc;&#136;sane helwasim.<BR>
Wam niyaz e le to, le xom le gi&#136;st kes&ecirc;<BR>
Pirsyar bikem:<BR>
Rast e awarey &#136;seqam &ucirc; hewrazekan,<BR>
&#136;S&ecirc;t&icirc; wu&#136;sey pirr le bar&ucirc;t,<BR>
Har&icirc; dil&icirc; pirr le agir, &ccedil;aw&icirc; niyan<BR>
Bend&icirc; nasor&icirc; bax&icirc; r&ucirc;t<BR>
Geyi&#136;stote n&ecirc;z&icirc;k&icirc; peyker&icirc; sip&icirc;?...
<BR>
Bawe&#136;s deda<BR>
Le bil&ecirc;sey agir&icirc; s&ucirc;r?<BR>
Wam niyaz e<BR>
Le to, le xom, le gi&#136;st kes&ecirc;<BR>
Pirsyar bikem.<BR>
Hawar bikem<BR>
Min dildar&icirc;m naw&ecirc; le naw<BR>
Bend&icirc;xaney asin&icirc;n da.<BR>
Le naw b&ecirc;&#136;ske w destraze da giyanim naw&ecirc;,<BR>
Janim naw&ecirc;,<BR>
Derdim naw&ecirc;.<BR>
Bo hetaw&ecirc;<BR>
Dem&icirc; helbest &ucirc; goran&icirc;m heldeh&ecirc;nim<BR>
Bims&ucirc;t&ecirc;n&ecirc;<BR>
Belam welam&icirc; pirsyarim bo bih&ecirc;n&ecirc;,<BR>
Bims&ucirc;t&ecirc;n&ecirc;<BR>
Belam lebat&icirc;y s&ecirc;ber,<BR>
Belam lebat&icirc;y s&ecirc;ber&icirc;<BR>
Pirr le bon &ucirc; pirr beramet<BR>
Tom bo b&ecirc;n&ecirc;!...<BR>
<BR>
<I>&#136;Sakel, 13.08.1971<BR>
<BR>
</I></FONT>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
