<BODY>
<H1>Ke to derroy<BR>
<BR>
</H1>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ke to derroy<BR>
Xem wek&ucirc; est&ecirc;reyek&icirc; zerd helgerraw<BR>
Le delaqey bir&icirc;newe<BR>
Derruwan&ecirc;te dil&icirc; ten&ecirc;m.<BR>
Ke to derroy<BR>
Wu&#136;sey xembar ser kiz deka w<BR>
Wurde wurde<BR>
Jani dil&icirc; dekate goran&icirc;y ew&icirc;n.<BR>
Ke to derroy honrawey &thorn;&icirc;n<BR>
Pena debate ber bir&icirc;n.<BR>
Ke to derroy<BR>
Pole wu&#136;sey cuwan &ucirc; &thorn;&icirc;r&icirc;n<BR>
Aram nagirin,<BR>
Laperrey zerd c&ecirc; deh&ecirc;lin,<BR>
Berew hewraz, berew l&ucirc;tke<BR>
Derron, dekewne helfirr&icirc;n...<BR>
Ke to derroy<BR>
Kej&icirc; h&icirc;wa le l&ucirc;tke we heta binar<BR>
Bo to degr&icirc;...<BR>
Kit&ecirc;b&icirc; bi&ccedil;kolekan&icirc; Kurdistan<BR>
Tij&icirc; debin le sir&ucirc;d&icirc; s&ucirc;r&icirc; xw&ecirc;n&icirc;n...
<BR>
Tifengekan de&#180;axin&icirc;n be gulley q&icirc;n.<BR>
<BR>
<I>Hamburg, 27.07.1978<BR>
<BR>
</I>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&copy; Ferhad Shakely<BR>
Ji <I>Kurdistan le dil&icirc; minda ye,</I> Invandrarf&ouml;rlaget,
Bor&aring;s, 1985, r. 76<BR>
