<H2><CENTER>&Ccedil;end r&ucirc;pel ji jiyana<BR>
<FONT SIZE=6>EREB &#136;SAM&Icirc;LOV<BR>
</FONT></CENTER></H2>
<H2><CENTER>Wez&icirc;r&ecirc; E&#136;so<BR>
</CENTER></H2>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<I>Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov yek ji niv&icirc;skar &ucirc; &#136;sexs&icirc;yet&ecirc;n
mezin y&ecirc;n Kurd&ecirc;n Sovyeta kevn e. &Ccedil;end roman
&ucirc; gelek niv&icirc;s li ser Kurdan niv&icirc;s&icirc;ne,
wek h&icirc;mdar&ecirc; romana Kurd&icirc; t&ecirc; nas&icirc;n
&ucirc; gelek roman niv&icirc;s&icirc;ne. L&ecirc; bel&ecirc;
heta ber&icirc; &ccedil;end salan j&icirc; nedihate zan&icirc;n
ku Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov ji al&icirc;y&ecirc; rej&icirc;ma
Stal&icirc;n de ji Ermen&icirc;stan&ecirc; hat&icirc;ye d&ucirc;r
xistin, di navbera sal&ecirc;n 1937-1954'an de tam 17 salan li
Sibiryay&ecirc; li derwar&icirc;y&ecirc; (exil) j&icirc;yaye.
Li vir bi jina xwe ya duwem&icirc;n Mar&icirc;ya Vas&icirc;levna
ve dibe nas ya ku di van b&icirc;ran&icirc;nan de nav&ecirc; w&ecirc;
derbas dibe, ew bi xwe Uris b&ucirc;ye, ew ke&ccedil;&ecirc;n
w&icirc; As&ecirc; &ucirc; Z&icirc;n&ecirc; ji v&ecirc; jina duwem&icirc;n
in. Jina w&icirc; ya ber&ecirc; Alman b&ucirc;ye. &Ccedil;awa
di van b&icirc;ran&icirc;n&ecirc;n j&ecirc;r de j&icirc; xuya
dibe, Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov di n&icirc;veka sal&ecirc;n 1950'y&icirc;
de veger&icirc;yaye Ermen&icirc;stan&ecirc;. Ev b&icirc;ran&icirc;n&ecirc;n
Wez&icirc;r&ecirc; E&#136;so, ji bo ron&icirc;kirina van sal&ecirc;n
nef&icirc;kirin&ecirc; wek dokumenteke dikare b&ecirc; hesib&icirc;n.
Niv&icirc;skar her &ccedil;iqas bi e&#136;skere, rast-rast qala
v&ecirc; b&ucirc;yera tradej&icirc;k nake j&icirc;, l&ecirc; bel&ecirc;
mirov ji van b&icirc;ran&icirc;nan &ccedil;end ti&#136;stan f&ecirc;r
dib&ecirc;, wek m&icirc;sal j&icirc;yana kesek&icirc; mehk&ucirc;mkir&icirc;
&ucirc; teze ji nef&icirc;b&ucirc;n&ecirc; veger&icirc;yaye. Niv&icirc;s
di demeke kr&icirc;t&icirc;k de hat&icirc;ye niv&icirc;s&icirc;n,
ber&icirc; serobina Sovyet&ecirc;. Ji ber v&ecirc; yek&ecirc;
j&icirc; mirov niv&icirc;skar fam dike. Niv&icirc;skar Wez&icirc;r&ecirc;
E&#136;so van sal&ecirc;n nef&icirc;kirin&ecirc; wek &quot;sal&ecirc;n
xer&icirc;b&icirc;y&ecirc;&quot; bi nav dike. Ev b&icirc;ran&icirc;nan
cara p&ecirc;&#136;s&icirc;n, di sala 1989'an de li Er&icirc;van&ecirc;
di berevokeke bi nav&ecirc; <B>Bahar</B> de hat&icirc;ye we&#136;sandin.
Nav&ecirc; niv&icirc;s&ecirc; y&ecirc; esl&icirc;n &quot;Rasthatin
tev&icirc; Ereb &#136;Semo&quot; ye. Di &icirc;mlaya niv&icirc;s&ecirc;
de min &ccedil;end guhartin&ecirc;n pi&ccedil;&ucirc;k j&icirc;
&ccedil;&ecirc;kirin.<BR>
</I>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<I><B>Rohat Alakom<BR>
<BR>
</B></I>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Nav&ecirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov hela h&ecirc; bi&ccedil;&ucirc;kt&icirc;y&ecirc;
de ber guh&ecirc; min ketib&ucirc;. L&ecirc; min ew, &ccedil;awa
div&ecirc;n, ne d&icirc;b&ucirc;, ne b&icirc;na b&ucirc;. Dema
ez b&ucirc;me xwendekar&ecirc; Un&icirc;vers&icirc;ta Er&icirc;van&ecirc;,
&ecirc;d&icirc; gelek caran nav&ecirc; w&icirc; ber min hildidan.
&Ucirc; ti&#136;stek&icirc; ec&ecirc;b &ucirc; hewaskar ew b&ucirc;
wek&icirc; ne ku ten&ecirc; wek&icirc;l, fikirdar &ucirc; intelleks&icirc;ya
Kurdan nav&ecirc; w&icirc; hildidan, ew b&icirc;r dian&icirc;n,
l&ecirc; wusan j&icirc; gund&icirc;y&ecirc;n sade, mirov&ecirc;n
kal &ucirc; p&icirc;r. &Ucirc; ewan bi hisret, hezkirin nav&ecirc;
w&icirc; hildidan. Ereb wexteke dir&ecirc;j b&ucirc; ne li Er&icirc;van&ecirc;
b&ucirc;, l&ecirc; niv&icirc;sar&ecirc;n w&icirc;, xazma &quot;<I>&#136;Sivan&ecirc;
Kurd</I>&quot; di nava cimaet&ecirc; de dihate b&icirc;ran&icirc;n&ecirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Hetan&icirc; hatina Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov min h&icirc;ml&icirc;
derheqa w&icirc; de ev gotin zanib&ucirc;n: ew h&icirc;mdarek&icirc;
edeb&icirc;yata Kurd ya Sovyet&ecirc;, zanek&icirc; d&icirc;rok,
edeb&icirc;yat, folklor &ucirc; etnografya cimaeta xwe ye, erheda
(welhasil) &#136;suxulkarek&icirc; cimaet&ecirc; (civat&ecirc;)
&ucirc; meden&icirc;yet&ecirc; y&ecirc; her&icirc; kiv&#136;s
e. Digotin, wek&icirc; ziman&ecirc; Kurd&icirc; pir rind zane,
lewz, zimanek&icirc; let&icirc;f&icirc; d&ecirc;v de ye. Hema
wusan j&icirc; digotin : &quot;Mala Ereb &#136;sewit&icirc;, ziman&ecirc;
har-maran d&ecirc;v de ne, kurmanc&icirc;ya ew zane k&icirc; zane!&quot;.
Digotin, wek&icirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov &ccedil;end ziman&ecirc;n
rohilat&ecirc; &ucirc; rojavay&ecirc; rind zane. Bi gotinek&ecirc;,
hetan&icirc; hatina &#136;Sam&icirc;lov &ucirc; heta d&icirc;tin&ecirc;
&ecirc;d&icirc; derheqa w&icirc; de fikreke gelek ba&#136;s li
bal min &ccedil;&ecirc;bib&ucirc; &ucirc; min di dil&ecirc; xwe
de digot: &quot;Gelo ew wext&ecirc; b&ecirc;, wek&icirc; ez bi
&ccedil;av&ecirc;n xwe w&icirc; emekdar&ecirc; meden&icirc;yeta
me bib&icirc;nim&quot;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&Ucirc; ew wext hat. Rojek&ecirc; min di rojnemeya &quot;<I>Sovetkan
Hayastan&quot;</I> de agahdar&icirc;ke Ajansa Ermen&icirc;s-tan&ecirc;
ya Telegraf&ecirc; ya resm&icirc; xwend, t&ecirc; de dihate gotin
ku bol&#136;sev&icirc;k&ecirc; kevin, niv&icirc;skar&ecirc; Kurd
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov veger&icirc;ya Ermen&icirc;stan&ecirc;.
Cimaeta Kurd, wusan j&icirc; ya Ermen&icirc;ya ew n&ucirc;&ccedil;eya
x&ecirc;r&ecirc; bi &#136;sab&ucirc;n qeb&ucirc;l kir. &Ucirc;
ez bi b&ecirc;sebir h&ecirc;v&icirc;ya w&ecirc; roj&ecirc; b&ucirc;m.
Dema ji min re w&ecirc; li hev b&ecirc;, bext&ecirc; min w&ecirc;
l&ecirc;xe, ez&ecirc; w&icirc; emekdar&ecirc; edeb&icirc;yata
me bib&icirc;nim &ucirc; ew roj j&icirc; hat.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
N&icirc;veka sal&ecirc;n 1950'y&icirc; redaks&icirc;yona rojnameya
<I>R&icirc;ya Teze </I>li avaya ser ku&ccedil;a <I>Karm&icirc;r
Banek&ecirc;</I> b&ucirc;. Ez tim&ecirc; di&ccedil;&ucirc;me wira.
Wek miqaledar, min informas&icirc;yon &ucirc; miqal&ecirc;n xwe
dibirin, yek&ecirc; j&icirc;, lawik did&icirc;tin, b&icirc;na
min ji wan derdiket.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Carek&ecirc; ez &ccedil;&ucirc;me redaks&icirc;yon&ecirc;, min
dixwast redaktor bib&icirc;nim. Min der&ecirc; oda w&icirc; vekir
&ucirc; dema min d&icirc;t mirovek li bal e &ucirc; ew dipey&icirc;vin,
min nexwast wan &#136;serpeze bikim &ucirc; hindav de der&icirc;
girt, pa&#136;sta veki&#136;s&icirc;yam. L&ecirc; bel&ecirc; redaktor
ez d&icirc;tim &ucirc; ez tekl&icirc;f&icirc; hundir kirim. Min
got&ecirc; wek&icirc; ez&ecirc; pa&#136;s&ecirc; b&ecirc;m. Ew
mirov&ecirc; nenas j&icirc; wek&icirc; pi&#136;sta w&icirc; min
de b&ucirc;, ser mil&ecirc; xwe zivir&icirc; &ucirc; li min nih&ecirc;r&icirc;.
Ez bi lez ji qat&ecirc; &ccedil;aran peyay&icirc; j&ecirc;r&ecirc;
b&ucirc;m &ucirc; &ecirc;d&icirc; ji avay&ecirc; 50-60 m&ecirc;troyan
d&ucirc;r ketib&ucirc;m. Min hew bih&icirc;st - yek w&ecirc; d&ucirc;rva
gaz&icirc; min dike &ucirc; nav&ecirc; min hildide. Ez pi&#136;st
xwe ve zivir&icirc;m: Eva M&icirc;kay&icirc;l&ecirc; Re&#136;s&icirc;d
e, rehmed&icirc; &#136;sa&icirc;r&ecirc; me &ucirc; wergervan&ecirc;
rojnamey&ecirc;. Ew hat g&icirc;hi&#136;ste min &ucirc; m&icirc;na
xwe hercar, bi heydade (heybet) got:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Kuro, pa&#136;sta bizvire, em herin redaks&icirc;yon&ecirc;,
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov gaz&icirc; te dike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ni&#136;sk&ecirc;va dil&ecirc; min kuta; ez &ccedil;awa &#136;sab&ucirc;me,
wek&icirc; mirovek&icirc; wusan navdar besa min, c&icirc;wan&ecirc;
xwendekar kir&icirc;ye, hewcey&icirc; d&icirc;tina min e. Heta
em gih&icirc;&#136;st&icirc;n c&icirc;h&ecirc;-c&icirc;h, hezar
&ucirc; yek fikir di ser&ecirc; min re derbas b&ucirc;n; gelo
&ccedil;ima gaz&icirc; min kir&icirc;ye? Divek yek&icirc; may&icirc;n
ez &#136;sibandibim? Ew j&icirc; naqewime, &ccedil;imk&icirc;
redaktor niha got&icirc;ye: ez k&icirc; me. Wusan e divek bav&ecirc;
min nas dike. L&ecirc; bel&ecirc; mena eyn&icirc; qet di fikra
min re derbas nedib&ucirc;. Ber der&ecirc; oda redaktor dil&ecirc;
min wusan l&ecirc; dixwist, te digot t&ecirc;, qefasa min der&ecirc;.
Hilki&#136;syab&ucirc;n &ccedil;ar qatan j&icirc; &quot;teqil&quot;
dab&ucirc; xebata dil&ecirc; min. Ez &ccedil;&ucirc;me hundir.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Keremke, r&ucirc;n&ecirc; Wez&icirc;r can, redaktor got, heval&ecirc;
&#136;Sam&icirc;lov dixwaze te bib&icirc;ne, bona w&ecirc; yek&ecirc;
me M&icirc;kay&icirc;l li pey xist.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez r&ucirc;ni&#136;st&icirc;m, rast p&ecirc;&#136;sber&icirc;
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov. Min ber&ecirc; hew zan&icirc;b&ucirc;
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov yek&icirc; govdek&icirc; bejnbilind e,
sim&ecirc;l&ecirc; re&#136;s y&ecirc;n palik&ecirc; (qalind) l&ecirc;.
L&ecirc; p&ecirc;&#136;sber&icirc; min mirovek&icirc; n&icirc;v&ccedil;e
r&ucirc;ni&#136;stib&ucirc;, &ccedil;evne gire, re&#136;se aqil
l&ecirc;, b&ecirc; r&ucirc; &ucirc; sim&ecirc;l.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- D&ecirc;mek, tu kur&ecirc; E&#136;so y&icirc;' Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
ji min pirs&icirc;, te digot me &ecirc;d&icirc; gelek&icirc; xeber
daye &ucirc; ew d&ucirc;mah&icirc;ya gotin&ecirc;n xwe t&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Bel&ecirc;, min got &ucirc; &#136;sermana xweydan&ecirc; ji
ser min re av&icirc;t.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- E&#136;soy&ecirc; Hut&icirc;
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Bel&ecirc;
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Mala we ji al&icirc;y&ecirc; Qers&ecirc;, ji gund&ecirc; &#136;Sir&icirc;nkoy&ecirc;
hat&icirc;ye?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Bel&ecirc; wusan dib&ecirc;jin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Hut&icirc; heye?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Na x&ecirc;r, &ccedil;&ucirc;ye rehmet&ecirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- L&ecirc; Xem, Xema p&icirc;rika te?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Dema ew&icirc; nav&ecirc; p&icirc;rka min hilda, gurz&icirc;y&ecirc;n
saw&ecirc; bedana min re derbas b&ucirc;n. Wek&icirc; ew&icirc;
nav&ecirc; kalk&ecirc; min zanib&ucirc;, ez ec&ecirc;bmay&icirc;
nemam, &ccedil;imk&icirc; Hut&icirc;y&ecirc; kalk&ecirc; mim mirovek&icirc;
navdar &ucirc; naskir&icirc; b&ucirc;. L&ecirc; dema nav&ecirc;
p&icirc;rka min hilda, ez &#136;sa&#136;s &ucirc; metel mam, wek&icirc;
pey ewqas salan re &ccedil;awa nav&ecirc; w&ecirc; b&icirc;r nekir&icirc;ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Reme li Hut&icirc; beg&ecirc;, Xem&ecirc; be, min nan&ecirc;
ber dest&ecirc; Xem&ecirc; gelek xwar&icirc;ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov h&ecirc;ja niha edil dest bi bi gotin&ecirc;n
xwe kir:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- H&ecirc;na &#136;Ser&ecirc; C&icirc;han&ecirc; y&ecirc; Yekem&icirc;n
b&ucirc;, l&ecirc; ber&icirc; reva 1918'an b&ucirc;. Ez w&ecirc;
dem&ecirc; li gund&ecirc; neh&icirc;ya D&icirc;gor&ecirc; ya Ezd&icirc;yan
diger&icirc;yam, min spartina Bol&#136;sev&icirc;kan diqedand,
bi kar&ecirc; &#136;sore&#136;s&ecirc; ve mij&ucirc;l dib&ucirc;m.
Derece wusan qewim&icirc; min got&icirc; xwe wedel&icirc; tada
(demeke derbasok) sepe bikira (ve&#136;sarta), ber &ccedil;av&ecirc;n
d&icirc;wana pad&#136;s&ecirc; neketama. &Ucirc; min biryar girt
xwe bav&ecirc;jim ber bext&ecirc; maleke kiv&#136;s, mirovek&icirc;
ba&#136;s. W&ecirc; h&ecirc;n&ecirc; mirovek&icirc; her&icirc;
navdar kalk&ecirc; te y&ecirc; rehmet&icirc; Hut&icirc; beg b&ucirc;.
Heb&ucirc;na w&icirc; ya giran tune b&ucirc;, l&ecirc; mirovek&icirc;
nandar, bilyan &ucirc; qedirgir b&ucirc;, nav&ecirc; begt&icirc;y&ecirc;
l&ecirc; kirib&ucirc;n, wek n&icirc;&#136;sana qedgirtin&ecirc;.
Lay&icirc;q&icirc; nav&ecirc; xwe b&ucirc;, ocaxa w&icirc; ocaxa
enzel (qonax) b&ucirc;, mala ber &ucirc; m&ecirc;vanan. Gelek&icirc;
bejna xwe hez dikir, papax&ecirc; kew, sapog&ecirc; xas, qay&icirc;&#136;s-qeme
gelek&icirc; bejna w&icirc; ya bilind, navkilka zirav dihatin.
Hut&icirc; beg yek&icirc; zer&icirc;n &ucirc; bedew b&ucirc;,
sim&ecirc;leke xwe&#136;s l&ecirc;b&ucirc;. Ez weke du mehan di
mala kalk&ecirc; te y&ecirc; rehmet&icirc; de mam. K&ecirc; &#136;sika
w&ecirc; yek&ecirc; bikira wek&icirc; &#136;sore&#136;sger, bol&#136;sev&icirc;k
di mala beg de xwe ve&#136;sart&icirc;ye. K&icirc; dikarib&ucirc;
ser sama (heybeta) Hut&icirc; beg&ecirc; biketa, bihata mala w&icirc;
bin&ecirc;r&icirc;ya. D&icirc;wan&ecirc;, dewlet&ecirc; ew nas
dikir, ew&icirc; bi nan&ecirc; xwe karker&ecirc;n dewlet&ecirc;
gi&#136;sk kor kirib&ucirc;n. Dema min di kox de niv&icirc;sara
xwe dikir, zarok&ecirc;n Hut&icirc; beg&ecirc; dahatin dora min,
heyr &ucirc; hejmetkar metelmay&icirc; li dest&ecirc; min, li
niv&icirc;sara min dinh&ecirc;r&icirc;n. De, feq&icirc;ra zanib&ucirc;n
niv&icirc;sar &ccedil;i ye? W&ecirc; h&ecirc;n&ecirc; dibistan
di gund&ecirc; kalk&ecirc; te de tune b&ucirc;, nava 16 gund&ecirc;
Ezd&icirc;yan de ten&ecirc; li Bacel&ucirc;y&ecirc; heb&ucirc;.
Er&ecirc;, zarok&ecirc;n Hut&icirc; pir n&icirc;n b&ucirc;n, ez
dib&ecirc;m kur &ucirc; q&icirc;zek b&ucirc;. Kur wek &ccedil;av&ecirc;n
xwe, delal&icirc; xwey&icirc; dikir, ew j&icirc; bi sapok b&ucirc;,
bi t&ecirc;leke poxikkir&icirc;. Kinc&ecirc;n here xas xwe &ucirc;
kur&ecirc; xwe re ji Qers&ecirc; dan&icirc;, heylo ji Tifl&icirc;s&ecirc;
dida an&icirc;n&ecirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Pa&#136;s&ecirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov pirsa xwendina min kir,
nefer&ecirc; mala me kir &ucirc; ez borcdar kirim, wek&icirc;
carek&ecirc; bav&ecirc; xwe b&icirc;nim bal w&icirc;; gelek&icirc;
dixwast kur&ecirc; Hut&icirc; beg&ecirc; bib&icirc;ne. Ez b&ecirc;jim;
xeyset&ecirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov wusan b&ucirc;; w&icirc;
tim&ecirc; dixwast mirov&ecirc;n sade, gund&icirc; &ucirc; bajarvan&ecirc;n
Kurd bib&icirc;ne, pirs &ucirc; pirs&icirc;yar&icirc;ka ji wan
bike. Vira c&icirc;h e b&ecirc; gotin&ecirc;, wek&icirc; pa&#136;swext&icirc;y&ecirc;
min ti&#136;stek&icirc; wa bal Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov texm&icirc;n
kir; eger rojek&ecirc; biqewim&icirc;ya, wek&icirc; kes&icirc;
Kurd mala w&icirc; neb&ucirc;ya m&ecirc;van, ew&ecirc; bi xwe
derketa, bi&ccedil;&ucirc;ya ku&ccedil;eke Er&icirc;van&ecirc;,
ya j&icirc; li ku&ccedil;a biger&icirc;ya, heta yek&icirc; ji
gund hat&icirc;, jin b&ucirc;ya m&ecirc;r b&ucirc;ya, bid&icirc;ta,
p&ecirc; re dipeyiv&icirc; &ucirc; h&ecirc;ja bi dilek&icirc;
baristan vediger&icirc;ya mala xwe.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Min got wek&icirc; pey&icirc; 40-50 salan re Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
nav&ecirc; p&icirc;rka min b&icirc;r nekirb&ucirc;. Lazim e bidim
kiv&#136;s&ecirc;, wek&icirc; ez pa&#136;swext&icirc;y&ecirc;
j&icirc; ser b&icirc;ra w&icirc; ec&ecirc;bmay&icirc; b&ucirc;m.
Ew&icirc; ne ku ten&ecirc; nav&ecirc; mirov&ecirc;n &ccedil;&ecirc;
ji<I> </I>b&icirc;r nedikir, l&ecirc; wusan j&icirc; zanib&ucirc;
f&ecirc;lankes, yan b&ecirc;vankes ji k&icirc;jan &ecirc;l&ecirc;
ye, k&icirc;jan qeb&icirc;l&ecirc; &ucirc; ber&ecirc;, ji mala
k&ecirc; ye, nev&icirc;y&ecirc; k&ecirc; ye, bi gotinek&ecirc;,
&ccedil;awa div&ecirc;n, heft govek bav&ecirc; w&icirc; j&icirc;
nas dikir. Bi v&icirc; tehr&icirc;, ew&icirc; bawer bik&icirc;,
hem&ucirc; Kurd&ecirc;n &Ecirc;zd&icirc; nas dikirin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ji rasthat&#155;n, d&icirc;tina p&ecirc;&#136;sin &#136;sundatir
min Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov gelek caran d&icirc;t, p&ecirc; re
qise kir. Komela niv&icirc;skaran de, rad&icirc;yoy&ecirc; de,
redaks&icirc;yona <I>R&icirc;ya Teze</I> de, Akedem&icirc;, k&ucirc;&ccedil;&ecirc;
de &ucirc; bext&ecirc; min heb&ucirc;ye gelek caran bibim m&ecirc;van&ecirc;
w&icirc;, oda w&icirc; ya xebat&ecirc; de, ber text&ecirc; sade,
ber ma&#136;s&icirc;na herfa ya pi&ccedil;&ucirc;k bib&icirc;nim.
Xeberdan, pirs-pirs&icirc;yar hez dikirin, l&ecirc; xeberdana
dir&ecirc;j hez nedikir. Dema &#136;sixul xelasb&ucirc;y&icirc;
hesab dikir, &ecirc;d&icirc; tu diday&icirc; femandin&ecirc;,
wek&icirc; lazime tu her&icirc;.<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<CENTER>***</CENTER>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Dema tu di&ccedil;&ucirc;y&icirc; mala Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
&ucirc; pay&ecirc; pir&icirc;n ew&icirc; bi xwe der&icirc; li
te vedikir. Bi be&#136;serek xwe&#136;s tu qeb&ucirc;l dikir&icirc;,
digot:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Ew tu y&icirc;, keremke, keremke wer&ecirc;. &Icirc;ro &#136;suxul&ecirc;
min li hev ket&icirc;ye, b&ecirc;je, ka &ccedil;i lazim e, &ccedil;i
al&icirc;y&ecirc; min dikeve?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Wusan lezo-bezo sivder&ecirc; de ji te re digot &ucirc; te &ecirc;d&icirc;
qursax ne dikir her&icirc; hundir.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- T&ecirc; her&icirc;? dema te kar&ecirc; &ccedil;&ucirc;y&icirc;n&ecirc;
dikir, ew&icirc; dipirs&icirc;: Ti&#136;stek&icirc; nake, careke
din&ecirc; were, em&ecirc; hinek&icirc; ji xwe re xeber bidin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Careke din di&ccedil;&ucirc;y&icirc;, d&icirc;sa tu bi be&#136;sereke
xwe&#136;s qeb&ucirc;l dikir&icirc; &ucirc; ji gotin&ecirc;n w&icirc;
y&ecirc;n p&ecirc;&#136;s&icirc;n kiv&#136;s dib&ucirc;, wek&icirc;
w&ecirc; te &ccedil;awa lazim e qeb&ucirc;l bike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
-Keremke, digot, w&icirc; tu ser &ccedil;evan re b&ecirc;y&icirc;,
were otaxa min, em hinek&icirc; gale-gala bikin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Em di&ccedil;&ucirc;ne otaxa w&icirc;. Li wir xenj&icirc; karyola
w&icirc;, dolava pirt&ucirc;kan &ucirc; text&ecirc; (masa) w&icirc;
y&ecirc; xebat&ecirc; tu ti&#136;stek&icirc; may&icirc;n tune
b&ucirc;, hem&icirc;n ma&#136;s&icirc;na w&icirc; ya &ccedil;apkirin&ecirc;
ya pi&ccedil;&ucirc;k tim&ecirc; li ser w&icirc; textey&icirc;
dan&icirc; b&ucirc;. Tim&ecirc; j&icirc; r&ucirc;pel&ecirc; n&icirc;vc&icirc;
herfr&ecirc;zkir&icirc; t&ecirc; de b&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
-E, &#136;Sam&icirc;lov ber text&ecirc; xwe, c&icirc;h&ecirc;
xwe y&ecirc; xebat&ecirc; y&ecirc; hergav r&ucirc;dini&#136;st,
tu j&icirc; hember&icirc; xwe diday&icirc; r&ucirc;ni&#136;standin&ecirc;
&ucirc; dest p&ecirc; dikir, de b&ecirc;je, qe hal-wext&ecirc;
te &ccedil;awa ye, zarok&ecirc;n te, jina te silamet in? Bav&ecirc;
te qe t&ecirc;?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Gi&#136;sk silamet in, em hem&ucirc; sax&icirc; &ucirc; silamet&icirc;ya
te dixwazin, min bers&icirc;va w&icirc; dida.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; te negot, bav&ecirc; te qe t&ecirc;?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Welle van daw&icirc;yan h&ecirc; nehat&icirc;ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Ca wek&icirc; t&ecirc;, ese (sed&icirc;-sed) b&icirc;ne mala
me, malavo, ez dixwazim kur&ecirc; H&ucirc;t&icirc; beg&ecirc;
bib&icirc;nim. Te eva &ccedil;end sal in soz daye, l&ecirc; hela
h&ecirc; neb&ucirc;y&icirc; xwey&ecirc; soza xwe.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Rast&icirc; j&icirc;, &#136;Sam&icirc;lov tim&ecirc; besa bav&ecirc;
min dikir. Ew&icirc; di j&icirc;y&icirc;n&ecirc; de bav&ecirc;
min ned&icirc;tib&ucirc;, diha rast ten&ecirc; pi&ccedil;&ucirc;kt&icirc;y&ecirc;
de, l&ecirc; &ccedil;awa kur&ecirc; nas&ecirc; w&icirc; y&ecirc;
hezkir&icirc; &ucirc; mirov&ecirc; bi salan mezin, dixwast bid&icirc;ta.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Pa&#136;s&ecirc; &#136;Sam&icirc;lov pirsa hal &ucirc; wext&ecirc;
Kurd&ecirc;n dereke dikir:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Ez heyrana te bim, ew zar&icirc;<B> </B>dib&ucirc;, m&icirc;na
ti&#136;stek&icirc; h&ecirc;v&icirc; bike, tu qet haj Kurmanc&ecirc;n
me hey&icirc;, gelo hal&ecirc; wan &ccedil;i ye?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Eger gotinek zanib&ucirc;ya, te j&ecirc; re digot, l&ecirc; eger
na, ew ber xwe diket. L&ecirc; w&icirc; zanib&ucirc;ya ese ji
te re digot.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Pa&#136;s&ecirc; pirsa ronakb&icirc;r&icirc;ya me, kar&ecirc;n
ocax&ecirc;n me y&ecirc;n meden&icirc;yet&ecirc; te dikir. Ti&#136;stek&icirc;
ne dil&ecirc; w&icirc; b&ucirc;ya, ese dida der. W&ecirc; &#136;sunda,
te hew din&ecirc;r&icirc;, &#136;Sam&icirc;lov ni&#136;sk&ecirc;va
xeberdan, gil&icirc;-gotin wusan tomer&icirc;, gulover dikirin,
wek&icirc; te bixwasta-nexwasta, rab&ucirc;yay&icirc;, bi&ccedil;&ucirc;yay&icirc;...
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Min pa&#136;s&ecirc;, dereng&icirc; mena b&icirc; xeyset&ecirc;
w&icirc; y&ecirc; ec&ecirc;b derxist. Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
gelek salan ne li Ermen&icirc;stan&ecirc; b&ucirc;ye, ji derec&ecirc;
meden&icirc;yeta civata me qet&icirc;yay&icirc; b&ucirc;ye. Loma
j&icirc; ew&icirc; hewl dida, m&icirc;na ti&#136;stek&icirc;,
wed&ecirc; wundakir&icirc; veger&icirc;ne. Ew gelek&icirc; dixebit&icirc;,
bawer bike hem&ucirc; seet&ecirc;n roj&ecirc;. Ma&#136;s&icirc;na
w&icirc; ya pi&ccedil;&ucirc;k li ber b&ucirc; &ucirc; w&icirc;
bi til&icirc;y&ecirc; xwe y&ecirc;n kalt&icirc;y&ecirc; y&ecirc;n
ziravb&ucirc;y&ecirc; teqe-teq l&ecirc; dixwast. Bi saya v&ecirc;
xebathez&icirc;y&ecirc;, v&ecirc; &#136;suxilkirina mezin b&ucirc;,
wek&icirc; di nava &ccedil;end salan de w&icirc; &ccedil;end efrandin&ecirc;n
pir-r&ucirc;pel niv&icirc;s&icirc;n &ucirc; dane we&#136;sandin&ecirc;.
Bi rast&icirc; j&icirc; w&icirc; heyfa xwe ji wed&ecirc; wundakir&icirc;<I>
</I>hilda. Bawer bik&icirc;, tu xwendekarek&icirc; Kurd&ecirc;n
dereke, ku li Moskovay&ecirc;, Len&icirc;ngrad&ecirc; h&icirc;n
dib&ucirc;n, tune b&ucirc;, ku bihata Ermen&icirc;stan&ecirc;,
Er&icirc;van&ecirc; &ucirc; mala Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov nemaya.
Carek&ecirc; min gotinek b&icirc;hist, go xortek&icirc; Kurd ji
Moskovay&ecirc; hat&icirc;ye, &ccedil;&ucirc;ye mala &#136;Sam&icirc;lov.
Ev&ecirc; te j&ecirc; re ezet-hurmet kir&icirc;ye &ucirc; di daw&icirc;y&ecirc;
de zor-zor sed manat &quot;serva&quot; kir&icirc;ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Tu xwendekar &icirc;, &#136;Sam&icirc;lov gotib&ucirc;ye, w&ecirc;
k&ecirc;r&icirc; te b&ecirc;n. Bel&ecirc; al&icirc;kar&icirc;
ten&ecirc; nedab&ucirc; w&icirc;...
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Carina j&icirc;, wed&ecirc; w&icirc; heb&ucirc;ya, masa ber te
dida rastkirn&ecirc;. Xwarina w&icirc; ya here hezkir&icirc; kebab
(&#136;s&icirc;&#136;slik) b&ucirc; an j&icirc; qel&icirc; b&ucirc;.
Gelek&icirc; ji go&#136;st&ecirc; p&ecirc;z hez dikir. Min j&ecirc;
derxistib&ucirc;, wek&icirc; &ccedil;av&ecirc;n xwe &icirc;lah&icirc;
y&ecirc;n neferan tu ti&#136;st&icirc; de nedih&icirc;&#136;st.
Carek&ecirc; ti&#136;stek&icirc; waha qewim&icirc;. Ez ji navbir&icirc;ya
xebat&ecirc; vediger&icirc;yama c&icirc;h&ecirc; xwe, rad&icirc;yoy&ecirc;.
Li qat&ecirc; sis&icirc;yan jina min sekin&icirc;b&ucirc;, h&ecirc;v&icirc;ya
min b&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- H&ecirc;ja mirovek&icirc; gund&icirc; li vira besa te dikir.
Ji lawik&ecirc;n redaks&icirc;yon&ecirc; dipirs&icirc;, min j&icirc;
&#136;serm kir n&ecirc;z&icirc;k bim.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- K&icirc; b&ucirc;, mirovek&icirc; &ccedil;awa b&ucirc;? Min
pirs&icirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Yek&icirc; n&icirc;v&ccedil;e, kal b&ucirc;, &#136;silyape (fotor)
s&ecirc;r&icirc; b&ucirc;. Ez &#136;sa&#136;s &ucirc; metel mam,
gund&icirc;y&ecirc; me y&ecirc;n niha j&icirc; rind xwe dikin,
ji bajarvan&icirc;ya ba&#136;stir.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Xwed&ecirc;, ez dil&ecirc; xwe de fikir&icirc;m, ew gund&icirc;y&ecirc;
m&icirc;na bajarvan&icirc;ya wergirt&icirc;ya k&icirc; ye? Min
&ccedil;iqas zor da hi&#136;s&ecirc; xwe, nikarib&ucirc; j&ecirc;
derxista.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Elbeke pi&ccedil;&ucirc;k j&icirc; d&ecirc;st de b&ucirc;, kulfeta
min ser de z&ecirc;de kir, tey&ecirc; qey bigota ez&ecirc; ji
w&ecirc; elb&ecirc; derxim, &ccedil;ika ew k&icirc; ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Xeberdan dev&ecirc; me de, jina min al&icirc;y&ecirc; nerdewana
nih&ecirc;r&icirc; &ucirc; bi heydade got:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Va ye, va hat!
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Ez fetil&icirc;m &ucirc; min bala xwe day&ecirc;, eva Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Q&icirc;z&ecirc;, Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- &Ccedil;i dib&ecirc;j&icirc;? kulfeta min &#136;sa&#136;s &ucirc;
metel ma.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Malavo, Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov b&icirc;n l&ecirc; &ccedil;ikyaye,
elba w&icirc; ya pi&ccedil;&ucirc;k d&ecirc;st de, d&ucirc;r ve
got, ez v&ecirc;sp&ecirc; de te digerim, tu ku y&icirc;?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Ez &ccedil;&ucirc;b&ucirc;m nav baj&ecirc;r, b&ecirc;y&icirc;
te ne lo&#136;s&icirc; can be, min nan xwar.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Ef&icirc;yet be, x&ecirc;reke j&ecirc; bib&icirc;n&icirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&#136;Sam&icirc;lov hat, p&ecirc;&#136;sber&icirc; me sekini &ucirc;
m&icirc;na hergav pirs&icirc;:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Pirsa edib t&ecirc; tune be, ke&ccedil;a min k&icirc; ye, kurmanc
e?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Bel&ecirc;, min bers&icirc;va w&icirc; da, kulfeta min e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov gelek &#136;sa b&ucirc;, dest p&ecirc;
kir pirs &ucirc; pirs&icirc;yar ji kulfeta min kir. &quot;Tu ji
k&icirc;der&ecirc; y&icirc;? D&ecirc; &ucirc; bav&ecirc; te mirov&ecirc;n
k&icirc;jan &ecirc;l&ecirc; ne, ji ku hatine&quot; &ucirc; gelek
pirs&ecirc; din&ecirc;. Kulfeta min ya belengaz soro-moro b&ucirc;b&ucirc;,
&ccedil;imk&icirc; nikarib&ucirc; bers&icirc;va pirsa w&icirc;
tam bide. Min d&icirc;t na, wa nabe, al&icirc;kar&icirc; day&ecirc;.
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov j&ecirc; re di nav &ccedil;end deqada
ewqas gil&icirc; derheqa d&icirc;roka &ecirc;la wan de, derheqa
Zuqur&icirc;ya &ucirc; Cang&icirc;r Axa de gotin, wek&icirc; divek
ew&ecirc; nava temam&icirc;ya emr&ecirc; xwe de neb&icirc;histib&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez&icirc; hinek&icirc; bal &#136;Sam&icirc;lov r&ucirc;vekir&icirc;
b&ucirc;m &ucirc; min j&ecirc; pirs&icirc;:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Eva &ccedil;i elb e?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Bavo, ew&icirc; dest p&ecirc; kir, gotin f&ecirc;za rad&icirc;yoy&ecirc;
kl&ucirc;bn&icirc;k stendine. Kl&ucirc;bn&icirc;kan re, ew zivir&icirc;
ser kulfeta min, kurmanc dib&ecirc;jin toqatk (&ccedil;&icirc;lek)
. Min got, ez herim zarokan re bikirim, ew j&icirc; bext&ecirc;
min re xelas bib&ucirc;n. De, ti&#136;ste nake, ez&ecirc; herim
ji s&ucirc;k&ecirc; bikirim. Ez ji vira veger&icirc;yam, biryar
da ku b&ecirc;m ser&icirc;k&icirc; te xim &ucirc; p&ecirc; bihesim,
ka van daw&icirc;yan &ccedil;ima wunda b&ucirc;y&icirc;, kiv&#136;s
nab&icirc;?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- &#136;Suxul-emel nah&ecirc;lin, apo, hema serh&ecirc;sa b&ucirc;m,
ez&ecirc; ese b&ecirc;m.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Q&icirc;za min j&icirc; b&icirc;ne, ese m&icirc;na ya bav&ecirc;
xwe nek&icirc;. Dema xatir&ecirc; we, min gelek&icirc; ser&ecirc;
we &ecirc;&#136;sand, Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov got &ucirc; &ccedil;&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Apo sebir ke ez&ecirc; b&ecirc;m te ver&ecirc;kim.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Na, ne lazim e, tu q&icirc;za min ver&ecirc;ke.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov &ccedil;&ucirc;, ez veger&icirc;yam &ucirc;
min dew ji kulfeta xwe kir:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Q&icirc;z&ecirc;, te ji &ccedil;i derxist, wek&icirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
gund&icirc; ye? Ne axir timt&ecirc;la (xeml) w&icirc; da tu ti&#136;stek&icirc;
gund&icirc;t&icirc;y&ecirc; tune.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- M&icirc;na gund&icirc;ya xeber dida, kulfeta min mena &#136;sab&ucirc;na
xwe eyan kir.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov &ccedil;iqas firnax dib&ucirc;,
&ccedil;ax&ecirc; dibih&icirc;st, wek&icirc; ke&ccedil;ek ya xortek&icirc;
Kurd &icirc;dareke xwendina bilind de hat&icirc;ye qeb&ucirc;l
kirin. Hindike em b&ecirc;jin, &#136;sa dib&ucirc;. K&ecirc; j&icirc;,
nas b&ucirc;ya, nenas b&ucirc;ya h&ecirc;v&icirc; ji &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
bikira, wek&icirc; bona qeb&ucirc;lkirin&ecirc; al&icirc;kar&icirc;y&ecirc;
bide, ew&icirc; xwe nedih&ecirc;vi&#136;sand, w&ecirc; kalt&icirc;ya
xwe p&ecirc;&#136;s&icirc;ya c&icirc;wanan, d&ecirc; &ucirc; bav&ecirc;
wan diket &ucirc; k&icirc;der&ecirc; lazim b&ucirc;ya, di&ccedil;&ucirc;y&ecirc;,
qedr&ecirc; xwe xerc dikir, carna bi h&ecirc;v&icirc;, rica dikir,
tek xort &ucirc; ke&ccedil;ek Kurd instut&icirc;y&ecirc; de b&ecirc;
qebulkirin&ecirc;. Ez bi xwe gelek xort &ucirc; ke&ccedil;&ecirc;
Kurd nas dikim y&ecirc;n ku bi al&icirc;kar&icirc;ya &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
institut, un&icirc;vers&icirc;te ya j&icirc; texn&icirc;kum&ecirc;
de qeb&ucirc;l b&ucirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov ne mirovek&icirc; qure, babax<B> </B>&ucirc;
kubar b&ucirc;. &Ccedil;awa cimaet dib&ecirc;je: &ccedil;&ucirc;kan
ra &ccedil;&ucirc;k, mezinan re mezin. L&ecirc; bi v&ecirc; re
tevay&icirc; qedr&ecirc; xwe rind zanib&ucirc;, xazma qedr&ecirc;
wan nav &ucirc; n&icirc;&#136;sanan, w&ecirc; s&icirc;yanet&ecirc;,
ya ku part&icirc;y&ecirc;, dewleta Sovyet&ecirc; dab&ucirc;ne
ser w&icirc;. Ew&icirc; gelek hez dikir b&icirc;r b&icirc;ne,
wek&icirc; nav&ecirc; proffesor&ecirc; sor li ser w&icirc; ye.
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov her cejnek&ecirc; de, her civ&icirc;n
&ucirc; &ecirc;var&icirc;k&ecirc; de p&ecirc;s&icirc;ra xwe bi
n&icirc;&#136;san &ucirc; madalya ve dixemiland. &Ucirc; div&ecirc;
b&ecirc; gotin&ecirc;, wek&icirc; mirov&ecirc; ku xeyset&ecirc;
w&icirc; rind zanib&ucirc;n, ew yek bi kubar&icirc;y&ecirc;, babax&icirc;y&ecirc;
re gir&ecirc; nedidan. Dema n&icirc;&#136;san &ucirc; madalya
p&ecirc;s&icirc;ra xwe dixistin, ne ku dixwast bi v&ecirc; yek&ecirc;
b&ecirc;je: &quot;Bala xwe bidin&ecirc;, ez &ccedil;ito mirov&quot;,
l&ecirc; daxwaza w&icirc; girtina qedr&ecirc; wan rewa b&ucirc;.
Ew bi wan n&icirc;&#136;san &ucirc; madalya ve firnax dib&ucirc;,
m&icirc;na zarokek&icirc; bi kinc&ecirc;n xwe &#136;sa dibe, ew
wusan &#136;sa dib&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov bav &ucirc; malxwek&icirc; xemk&ecirc;&#136;s
b&ucirc;. Ew&icirc; qedr&ecirc; kulfeta xwe Mar&icirc;ya Vas&icirc;levnay&ecirc;
gelek&icirc; zanib&ucirc;. Dema ez di&ccedil;&ucirc;m m&ecirc;van&icirc;ya
w&icirc; &ucirc; kulfeta w&icirc; li ort&ecirc; hazir b&ucirc;ya,
te hew din&ecirc;r&icirc; ni&#136;sk&ecirc;va digot:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Meta te kulfeteke &#136;s&icirc;rhelal e, ew n&icirc;n b&ucirc;ya,
divek ez niha sax n&icirc;nb&ucirc;ma. Ew&ecirc; roj&ecirc; &ccedil;etin
de gelek al&icirc;kar&icirc; daye min, ez keda w&ecirc; nikarim
b&icirc;r bikim.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Mar&icirc;ya Vas&icirc;levnay&ecirc; j&icirc; al&icirc;y&ecirc;
xwe de gelek&icirc; xemxur b&ucirc; himber&icirc; w&icirc;. Min
tim&ecirc; texm&icirc;n dikir, wek&icirc; ew sib&ecirc; heta &ecirc;var&ecirc;,
&ccedil;awa dib&ecirc;n, totanga (kes&ecirc; t&ecirc;-di&ccedil;e)
w&icirc; ye, w&ecirc; p&icirc;rt&icirc; &ucirc; b&ecirc;sehet&icirc;ya
xwe, &ccedil;awa cimaet dib&ecirc;, m&icirc;na destmaleke ser
desta qulix&ecirc; w&icirc; de ne. Min hertim t&ecirc; derdixist,
wek&icirc; Mar&icirc;ya Vas&icirc;levnay&ecirc; hez nedikir, dema
m&ecirc;van gelek&icirc; r&ucirc;dini&#136;stin &ucirc; m&ecirc;r&ecirc;
w&ecirc; mij&ucirc;l dikirin. Ew&ecirc; nedixwast, wek&icirc;
bi xeberdana dir&ecirc;j kar&ecirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov &#136;serpeze
bikin, ew&icirc; ji xebata efrandar&icirc;y&ecirc; bibirin yan
j&icirc; aciz bikin. Bona saxlem&icirc;ya w&icirc; gelek xemxur
b&ucirc;. Ji &quot;tirsa&quot; w&ecirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
new&ecirc;rib&ucirc; e&#136;skere cixar&ecirc; bik&#136;s&icirc;ne.
Dema ez di&ccedil;&ucirc;m mala wan, ew&icirc; tim&ecirc; ez tekl&icirc;f&icirc;
oda xwe dikirim, der&icirc; li ser me de digirt &ucirc; dest&ucirc;r
dida ez cixar&ecirc; bik&#136;s&icirc;nim, wek&icirc; ew j&icirc;
bikaribe &quot; tald&ecirc;&quot; min de duy&ecirc; cixarek&ecirc;
hecam<B> </B>bike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov gelek&icirc; ewled&ecirc;n xwe hez dikir.
Ke&ccedil;a w&icirc; Meyan&ecirc; z&ucirc;va m&ecirc;r kirib&ucirc;.
Herdu ke&ccedil;&ecirc;n pi&ccedil;&ucirc;k bal w&icirc; b&ucirc;n,
di van sal&ecirc;n daw&icirc;n de m&ecirc;r kirin. Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
nav&ecirc; Kurmanc&icirc; li van herda kirib&ucirc;; nav&ecirc;
yek&ecirc; As&ecirc; b&ucirc;, ya din&ecirc; Z&icirc;n&ecirc;,
nav&ecirc; m&ecirc;rxasa destana Ehmed&ecirc; Xan&icirc; &ucirc;
beyt-serhat&icirc;ya cimaet&ecirc; &quot;Mem &ucirc; Z&icirc;n
&quot;. Ew&icirc; herdu ke&ccedil; j&icirc; g&icirc;handin miraz&ecirc;
wan, kirin xwey&ecirc; xwendina bilind.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez carek&ecirc; &ccedil;&ucirc;me mala wan, l&ecirc; herdu ke&ccedil;
j&icirc; ne li mal b&ucirc;n. Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov ji min
pirs&icirc;:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Te ke&ccedil;ik&ecirc;n min d&icirc;tine?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- &Ccedil;awa ned&icirc;tine!
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- L&ecirc; van daw&icirc;yan?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Na, min got&ecirc;, van &ccedil;end sal&ecirc;n pa&#136;sin
min ned&icirc;tine.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- De tu kerama xwe sebir bike, Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov got &ucirc;
ji oda xwe derket. Lezek&icirc; &#136;sunda w&ecirc;neyek d&ecirc;st
de ew veger&icirc;ya.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Eva w&ecirc;n&ecirc; wan y&ecirc; her&icirc; pa&#136;sin e,
&ccedil;endek&icirc; p&ecirc;&#136;sta tevay&icirc; ki&#136;sandin,
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov got &ucirc; w&ecirc;ne dir&ecirc;j&icirc;
min kir.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Min bala xwe day&ecirc;, herdu x&ucirc;&#136;sk li p&icirc;ya
li rex hev sekin&icirc;b&ucirc;n &ucirc; ti&#136;stek&icirc; hewaskar,
herda j&icirc; kinc&ecirc; kurmanc&icirc;, rihal&ecirc; millet&icirc;y&ecirc;
wergirtib&ucirc;n, kof&icirc;-kitan, d&ecirc;re &ucirc; &ecirc;lek&ecirc;
cimaeta me.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov bi &#136;sab&ucirc;n hey&icirc; li min
dinih&ecirc;r&icirc;, hey&icirc; li w&ecirc;n&ecirc; ewled&ecirc;
xwe y&ecirc;n hezkir&icirc;. Min texm&icirc;n kir, wek&icirc;
ew gelek&icirc; bi wana firnax dibe &ucirc; xazma bi w&ecirc;
yek&ecirc;, wek&icirc; qe na, di w&ecirc;ne de ewan bi kinc&ecirc;
millet&icirc;y&ecirc; t&ecirc;ne xuyan. B&ecirc;y&icirc; gotina
min, niv&icirc;skar&ecirc; hezkir&icirc; ew w&ecirc;ne p&ecirc;&#136;sk&ecirc;&#136;s&icirc;
min kir.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; ke&ccedil;&ecirc;n Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov ten&ecirc;
bona ki&#136;sandina w&ecirc;ne kinc &ucirc; rihal&ecirc; millet&icirc;y&ecirc;
wernedigirtin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Carek&ecirc; ez &ccedil;&ucirc;me d&icirc;lanek&ecirc;. Ew d&icirc;lan
li Er&icirc;van&ecirc; b&ucirc;. Rreb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov hatib&ucirc;
&ucirc; ke&ccedil;a xwe Z&icirc;n&ecirc; j&icirc; bi xwe re anib&ucirc;.
Z&icirc;n&ecirc; kinc&ecirc; kurmanc&icirc;y&ecirc; wergirtib&ucirc;n.
Dema ew &ucirc; bav&ecirc; ve ketin govend&ecirc;, min texm&icirc;n
kir, wek&icirc; Z&icirc;n&ecirc; qayd&ecirc; kurmanc&icirc;y&ecirc;
rind dil&icirc;ze. Bav&ecirc; ew h&icirc;n kirib&ucirc;.<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<CENTER>***<BR>
</CENTER>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Rojek&ecirc; p&ecirc; his&icirc;yam wek&icirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
likum&icirc;ye &ucirc; ling&ecirc; w&icirc; guzik&ecirc; de &#136;sikest&icirc;ye.
Eva j&icirc; beseke ne bi x&ecirc;r b&ucirc;, &ccedil;imk&icirc;
d&icirc;yare e, wek&icirc; hestuy&ecirc; kal &ucirc; p&icirc;ran
y&ecirc;n &#136;sikest&icirc; dereng ya j&icirc; &ccedil;etin
diceribe. Ez serda &ccedil;&ucirc;m. H&ecirc;v&icirc;y&ecirc;
b&ucirc;m, wek&icirc; ez&ecirc; w&icirc; halek&icirc; mel&ucirc;l
&ucirc; sex&icirc;r de bib&icirc;nim. L&ecirc; d&icirc;sa ew Ereb
&#136;Sam&icirc;lov&ecirc; wek ber&ecirc; b&ucirc;, ten&ecirc;
wekez (gopal) girtib&ucirc; xwe &ucirc; ling&ecirc; w&icirc; gir&ecirc;day&icirc;,
ser al&ccedil;&icirc;y&ecirc; de, p&ecirc;&ccedil;ay&icirc; b&ucirc;.
Dewsa ez ber dil&ecirc; w&icirc; da b&ecirc;m, ew ber dil&ecirc;
min &ucirc; kulfeta xwe de hat.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Ti&#136;stek&icirc; nake, ew&icirc; b&ecirc;minet got, malavano,
w&ecirc; biceribe. Doxtora got, wek&icirc; xurek&ecirc; rind bixw&icirc;,
w&ecirc; z&ucirc; biceribe.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez &#136;sa&#136;s &ucirc; metel&ecirc; v&ecirc; b&icirc;nfireh&icirc;ya
w&icirc; mam. Divek hema v&icirc; xeyset&icirc; ew &ucirc; saxlem&icirc;y&ecirc;
ve xwey&icirc; kirin, dema ew gelek salan li xer&icirc;b&icirc;y&ecirc;
b&ucirc;, di nav merc&ecirc;n hema xirab de dixebit&icirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Dema ez derketim &ecirc;d&icirc; m&icirc;na hercar, &#136;Sam&icirc;lov
ez ver&ecirc; nekirim. Kulfeta w&icirc; der&icirc; li ber min
vekir &ucirc; dema xal-xatir&ecirc; ez ber dil&ecirc; w&ecirc;
de hatim, ew gir&icirc;ya &ucirc; bi kelogir&icirc; ji min re
got:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
- Na, Wez&icirc;r, Ereb&ecirc; ji v&icirc; ling&icirc; here. Gelek
c&icirc;hek&icirc; &ccedil;etin, g&ucirc;zik&ecirc; de &#136;sikest&icirc;ye.
Ew &ccedil;i zulm b&ucirc;, Ereb&ecirc; sap&icirc; silamet...
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&Ucirc; &ecirc;d&icirc; nikarib&ucirc; xeber bida.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez d&icirc;sa li ber dil de hatim &ucirc; &ccedil;&ucirc;m.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov ji ling, ji &#136;sikestina
hestu nemir. Dil&ecirc; w&icirc; sekin&icirc;. Ew dil&ecirc; ku
bina serketina xebata Len&icirc;n, Oktobra Mezin &ucirc; azad&icirc;,
bextewar&icirc;ya cimaet&ecirc; li Qers&ecirc; &ucirc; Sar&icirc;qam&icirc;&#136;s&ecirc;,
li Kafkasa &#136;Simal&ecirc; &ucirc; Len&icirc;ngrad&ecirc;,
li Moskovay&ecirc; &ucirc; Er&icirc;van&ecirc;, li pala &ccedil;&icirc;yay&ecirc;
Elegez&ecirc; &ucirc; Axmixan&ecirc;, gelek c&icirc; &ucirc; waran
kuta b&ucirc;, l&ecirc; xistib&ucirc; &ucirc; niha, dema &ecirc;d&icirc;
west&icirc;ya b&ucirc;, pey&icirc; qedandina r&ecirc;ke dir&ecirc;j
ya s&icirc;yanet re sekin&icirc;. L&ecirc; kar&ecirc;n w&icirc;,
efrandin&ecirc;n w&icirc; man bona cimaet&ecirc;, bona dil&#136;sah&icirc;ya
mirovan.<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<I>Transkripsiyona ji Kir&icirc;l&icirc;: Rohat Alakom</I>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&copy; Wez&icirc;r&ecirc; Eso
</BLOCKQUOTE>
