<HTML>
<HEAD>
<META HTTP-EQUIV="Content-Type" CONTENT="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1">
<TITLE> Lkoln</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.03z">
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<HR>
<H2><CENTER>L&ecirc;kol&icirc;n</CENTER></H2>
<H2><CENTER><FONT SIZE=6>Niv&icirc;skar&ecirc; kurd, &ccedil;anda
kurd&icirc; &ucirc; pirsa nasnamey&ecirc;<BR>
</FONT><FONT SIZE=5>Hendir&ecirc;n</FONT></CENTER></H2>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ev &ucirc; &ccedil;end pirsgir&ecirc;k &ucirc; asteng&ecirc;n
d&icirc;tir &ecirc;n tozgirt&icirc;; eger li ser bingeha herifandineke
sazkar; bi n&ecirc;r&icirc;neke teor&icirc; &ucirc; bi t&ecirc;gihi&thorn;tineke
n&ucirc;jen, ney&ecirc;n wergerandin &ucirc; &ccedil;areserkirin;
d&ecirc; nasnameya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me &ucirc; tengahiy&ecirc;n
siyas&icirc;-m&ecirc;j&ucirc;y&icirc; li beramber&icirc; pirs
&ucirc; guman&ecirc;n tevl&icirc;hev &ecirc;n c&icirc;han&ecirc;;
d&ecirc; hejar &ucirc; b&ecirc; peyam bim&icirc;nin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Wek serencam, eger em wisa nekin; d&ecirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
me p&ecirc;rg&icirc; namoy&icirc; (ixt&icirc;rab) &ucirc; tengatiyeke
navxwey&icirc; ya gir&ecirc;kk&ucirc;r bibe. Jixwe namoy&icirc;
&ucirc; tenhatiya mirovan j&icirc;; bi xwesipartina li ser palpi&thorn;t
&ucirc; nasnameya &ccedil;andey&icirc;, mirovan ber bi jiyaneke
tevl&icirc;hev &ucirc; b&ecirc; berpirsyar&icirc; ve radiki&thorn;&icirc;ne,
ango jiyanek li dervey&icirc; b&ucirc;neweriya heb&ucirc;n&ecirc;;
jiyana b&ecirc; armanc &ucirc; jiyana mirina amadekir&icirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Li vir, ji bo germkirina v&ecirc; real&icirc;teya westiyay&icirc;;
em&ecirc; &ccedil;end pirs&ecirc;n sade; l&ecirc; p&ecirc;wist,
li ber &ccedil;av&ecirc;n &ccedil;and &ucirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n
me, rax&icirc;nin:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&Icirc;ro, di nava xirecira b&ucirc;yeran de; &ucirc; di nava
guhertin&ecirc;n &ccedil;erxane y&ecirc;n c&icirc;han&ecirc; de;
li beramber&icirc; teq&icirc;na felsefey&ecirc; &ucirc; ragihandin&ecirc;n
ku li ser bidaw&icirc;hatina d&icirc;rok&ecirc; dipeyivin; li
beramber&icirc; t&ecirc;k&ccedil;&ucirc;na nirx &ucirc; prens&icirc;p&ecirc;n
p&icirc;roz &ecirc;n idyolojyay&ecirc; &ucirc; li beramber&icirc;
bikaran&icirc;na hem&icirc; be&thorn;&ecirc;n zanist &ucirc; tiknolojya
&ucirc; &thorn;aristaniy&ecirc;; &ucirc; namob&ucirc;n &ucirc;
westana mirovatiy&ecirc; li hember v&ecirc; bikaran&icirc;n&ecirc;,
&icirc;ro; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n me, y&ecirc;n ber&ecirc;
&ucirc; y&ecirc;n aniha, bi &ccedil;i away&icirc;; di k&icirc;jan
sewiyet&ecirc; de be&thorn;dar&icirc; w&ecirc; rew&thorn;&ecirc;
b&ucirc;ne? Rola rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n kurd di v&ecirc;
p&ecirc;vajoy&ecirc; de &ccedil;i ye?. Herwisa; n&ecirc;r&icirc;na
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n me bo xwendin &ucirc; anal&icirc;zkirina
wan r&ecirc;baz &ucirc; m&icirc;tod &ucirc; hizr &ucirc; felsefeyan
&ucirc; r&ucirc;danan &ccedil;i b&ucirc; &ucirc; &ccedil;i ye?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Deq&ecirc;n felsef&icirc; &ucirc; teor&icirc; &ucirc; hizr &ucirc;
raman&ecirc;n rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n me; li beramber&icirc;
wan b&icirc;r&ucirc;baweriy&ecirc;n w&ecirc;jey&icirc; y&ecirc;n
gelemper; y&ecirc;n mi&thorn;t aferandin &ucirc; dah&ecirc;nan;
herwilo, wergerandina w&icirc; &ucirc; &ccedil;awatiya w&icirc;;
di k&icirc;jan sewiyet&ecirc; de ne?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi van pirs&ecirc;n sade l&ecirc; p&ecirc;wist; em dikarin d&ucirc;rb&icirc;niya
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd binirx&icirc;nin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Digel v&ecirc; j&icirc;, gerek em li nik deng&ecirc;n takekesane;
y&ecirc;n ku hewl didin ku c&icirc;han&ecirc; &ucirc; Kurdistan&ecirc;
bi m&icirc;kan&icirc;zima awez (aqil) bixw&icirc;nin, &ucirc;
&ccedil;engek ji t&ecirc;rm&ecirc;n giran, di v&icirc; war&icirc;
de, bi kar t&icirc;nin, rawestin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi baweriya min, ev hewldan, bi gi&thorn;t&icirc;, xwe disp&ecirc;re
du dengan: Deng&ecirc; yekem structulism e &ucirc; y&ecirc; diwem
j&icirc; tevlihevkirina suryal&icirc;zm &ucirc; formalizm &ucirc;
raportizm&ecirc; ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Hewldana p&ecirc;&thorn;&icirc;n ji ya daw&icirc;n &ccedil;alaktir
&ucirc; k&ucirc;rtir e, &ccedil;ink&icirc; ya diwem&icirc;n &thorn;&ecirc;wexwaz
e; ten&ecirc; di helbest&ecirc; de peyda dibe; bi r&ecirc;baziyeke
zelal &ucirc; e&thorn;kere napeyive, lewra &ccedil;alakiy&ecirc;n
w&ecirc; k&ecirc;mtir dixuyin. Bi gi&thorn;t&icirc;; ev herd&ucirc;
hewldan hetan&icirc; aniha di s&icirc;nor&ecirc; destegiriy&ecirc;
(gir&ucirc;piy&ecirc;) de &ucirc; li du bajaran (Hewl&ecirc;r
&ucirc; Sul&ecirc;mani) t&ecirc;n naskirin, Van herd&ucirc; hewldanan
digel aliy&ecirc;n xwe y&ecirc;n er&ecirc;t&icirc; (pozitiv) j&icirc;,
&ccedil;end b&icirc;r&ucirc;baweriy&ecirc;n nayet&icirc; wek hewl&ecirc;r&icirc;t&icirc;
&ucirc; sil&ecirc;man&icirc;t&icirc;, dirust kirine. Ev s&icirc;ma
bixwe j&icirc; vedigere rewi&thorn;t&ecirc;n her&icirc; pa&thorn;may&icirc;
y&ecirc;n civata me bi gi&thorn;t&icirc; &ucirc; rewi&thorn;ta
naskir&icirc; ya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me bi taybet&icirc;.
Hi&thorn;mendiyek wisa ji berhemdariya gundiyane ya civata me
&ucirc; ji bi &thorn;&ucirc;ndemay&icirc;na destegeriy&ecirc;,
t&ecirc;, &ucirc; c&icirc;hana rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me
y&ecirc; naskir&icirc; n&icirc;gar dike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
B&ecirc;guman rew&thorn;a taybet&icirc; ya pi&thorn;t&icirc; sala
1991 &ecirc; li Kurdistan&ecirc; di bin siya herd&ucirc; partiy&ecirc;n
desthilat de, peyda b&ucirc;b&ucirc;, digel &ccedil;end faktor&ecirc;n
siyas&icirc;, abor&icirc;, komelayet&icirc;, sinc&icirc;, ps&icirc;koloj&icirc;
ku li vir ne cih&ecirc; liserawestan&ecirc; ne, wek faktoreke
&ccedil;ewt, li ser wan herd&ucirc; hewldanan &ucirc; li ser p&ecirc;vajoya
taze ya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me, dirust b&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; van herd&ucirc; partiy&ecirc;n siyas&icirc; di demeke
pir kurt de dikar&icirc;b&ucirc;n bi al&icirc;kariya peran &ucirc;
deshilatdariya xwe wan rew&thorn;enb&icirc;ran bixes&icirc;nin
&ucirc; hem&icirc; dezgeh &ucirc; hem&icirc; deng&ecirc;n rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;
y&ecirc;n takekes (ferd&icirc;) &ecirc;n ku hewldana tazegeriy&ecirc;
dikirin, best bikin; gem bikin. Herwisa hem&icirc; h&ecirc;z &ucirc;
kar&icirc;n &ucirc; germahiya ku di la&thorn;&ecirc; wan rew&thorn;enb&icirc;ran
de heb&ucirc; ji bo alav&ecirc;n ragihandina partiy&ecirc;n xwe
bi kar an&icirc;n. Ji ni&thorn;k&ecirc; ve &ucirc; pi&thorn;t&icirc;
demeke kurt meydan &ucirc; c&icirc;hana rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;
ber bi sist&icirc; &ucirc; erzan&icirc; &ucirc; lawaziy&ecirc;
de di&ccedil;e, ji bo berjewendiy&ecirc;n herd&ucirc; partiyan
t&ecirc;t bi kar an&icirc;n. Hem&icirc; &ccedil;apxane ji bo armanc&ecirc;n
partiyan dest bi xebat&ecirc; dikin, wek ku &ccedil;awan bajar
&ucirc; gund di navbera partiy&ecirc;n Kurdistan&ecirc; de hatin
dabe&thorn;kirin wisa j&icirc; &ucirc; bi heman &thorn;&ecirc;wey&icirc;
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n kurd. Bi kurt&icirc;, &thorn;&ucirc;n&thorn;op
&ucirc; bikaran&icirc;n&ecirc;n siyas&icirc; sinc&icirc; y&ecirc;n
ku ji al&icirc; Basiy&ecirc;n Iraq&ecirc; dihatin p&ecirc;kan&icirc;n;
v&ecirc; car&ecirc; bi awak&icirc; pir sade &ucirc; kawikane,
bi riya partiyan, &ucirc; bi xwesipartina li ser diru&thorn;mey&ecirc;n
kurdayet&icirc;, b&ecirc;y&icirc; r&ecirc;bazeke raman&icirc;,
ten&ecirc; ji boy&icirc; diqdiqandina hest&ecirc;n rew&thorn;enb&icirc;ran,
xwe d&ucirc;bare dikirin da ku cil&ecirc; ji bin ling&ecirc;n
wan bi&thorn;emit&icirc;nin, wan bixap&icirc;nin. B&ecirc;guman
di v&ecirc; p&icirc;lan&ecirc; de, herd&ucirc; part&icirc;, ba&thorn;
bi serketin. Wek serencam; berpirsiyariya v&ecirc; rew&thorn;&ecirc;
nakeve hust&ecirc; ti al&icirc; &ucirc; ti partiyan; biqas&icirc;
ku &ccedil;iyet&icirc; &ucirc; sewiyeta hi&thorn;yar&icirc; ya
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me, wek du regezan, rola xwe ya bingeh&icirc;n
di serkeftina v&ecirc; proses&ecirc; de l&icirc;stiye, &ccedil;ink&icirc;
gotara desthilatiy&ecirc;, navend &ucirc; al&icirc;giriya partiyane
bixwe, hi&thorn;yar&icirc; &ucirc; str&ucirc;kt&ucirc;ra rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r
&ucirc; &ccedil;anda me bi gi&thorn;t&icirc; dadimezir&icirc;nin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me, di van bar&ucirc;doxan de, wek
gotara d&icirc;magoj&icirc; ya partiy&ecirc;n me &ucirc; alav&ecirc;n
rag&icirc;handina partiyane, eger ne part&icirc; be, al&icirc;gir
e yan j&icirc; berdestek&icirc; dilsoj bo partiyan e, bi al&icirc;kariya
bikaran&icirc;na &ccedil;end t&ecirc;rm&ecirc;n wek modern&icirc;zm
&ucirc; zanist &ucirc; felsefe &ucirc; hemdem&icirc; jiyana xwe
ya li ber dest&ecirc; partiyan didom&icirc;nin, di wextek&ecirc;
de ku yek ji van t&ecirc;rman di wateya xwe y&icirc; resen de,
li ba me ne t&ecirc;t bi kar an&icirc;n &ucirc; ne j&icirc; t&ecirc;t
gunc&icirc;n, &ccedil;ink&icirc; ne deq&ecirc;n wan ramyar &ucirc;
f&ecirc;losof &ucirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;ran hene da ku wan t&ecirc;rman
bi&ccedil;esip&icirc;nin &ucirc; ne j&icirc; zem&icirc;na van
t&ecirc;rman di hi&thorn; &ucirc; avahiya civat &ucirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
me de heye. Li dervey&icirc; v&ecirc; rastiy&ecirc; j&icirc;;
ew &ccedil;end deq &ucirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n ku peyda
dibin j&icirc;, b&ecirc;agah&icirc; di tenhatiy&ecirc; de dij&icirc;n
&ucirc; b&ecirc; maf in &ucirc; devgemkir&icirc; ne, ev deq &ucirc;
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r diyar &ucirc; e&thorn;kere ne lewra p&ecirc;wist
nake ku em li ser wan rawestin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi herhal eger ew real&icirc;teya aloz a &ccedil;anda me ya ku
em li ser dipeyivin b&ecirc; bandor an k&ecirc;m bandor be j&icirc;
d&icirc;sa pirsa n&ucirc;jen&icirc; &ucirc; tazegeriya me y&icirc;
&icirc;ro xwe ferz dike digel tuneb&ucirc;na &ccedil;avkaniy&ecirc;n
&ccedil;anda c&icirc;han&icirc;. &Icirc;ca bingeha wan hewldan&ecirc;n
n&ucirc;jen &ucirc; taze, diyardeya wergerandina deq&ecirc;n balk&ecirc;&thorn;
&ucirc; nemir di &ccedil;ar&ccedil;ewa guheztin &ucirc; destewayiya
r&ecirc;baz &ucirc; bizav&ecirc;n ziman&ecirc;n d&icirc;tir &ecirc;n
dunyay&ecirc; de &ucirc; li dervey&icirc; nav&ccedil;eya me dim&icirc;nin.
Ma gelo b&ecirc;y&icirc; heb&ucirc;n &ucirc; peydab&ucirc;na wan
deq &ucirc; &ccedil;avkaniyan bi ziman&ecirc; kurd&icirc; em dikarin
b&icirc;r &ucirc; baweriy&ecirc;n r&ecirc;baz&ecirc;n c&icirc;han&icirc;
t&ecirc;bigih&ecirc;jin? Lewra beriya ku em di guheztin &ucirc;
destewayiya n&ucirc;jeniy&ecirc; de biramin, gerek em bi&thorn;&ecirc;n
bi al&icirc;kariya wergerandin&ecirc; naveroka teor&icirc; ya
wan r&ecirc;bazan binasin. Ma &ccedil;awan b&ecirc;y&icirc; v&ecirc;
zem&icirc;na hi&thorn;yariyane d&ecirc; tazeger&icirc; b&ecirc;
avakirin madam pi&thorn;t&icirc;neya (xelfiyeta) rew&thorn;enb&icirc;riya
me &ucirc; meydana hi&thorn;yar&icirc; &ucirc; zaneyariya me li
dervey&icirc; xwendina Hegel &ucirc; Marks &ucirc; Nit&thorn;&ecirc;,
Haydgar, kirkgard, sartre, Sp&icirc;noza, Dreda, &THORN;traws
&ucirc; Part &ucirc; Ba&thorn;lar &ucirc; Delouz p&ecirc;k hatiye?
&Ccedil;awan ten&ecirc; bi xwendina Fouco em d&ecirc; bikaribin
strak&thorn;ral&icirc;zm&ecirc; &ucirc; prosesa k&ucirc;r &ucirc;
tevlihev a felsefeya b&ucirc;neweriya d&icirc;roka ku bi rew&thorn;a
abor&icirc; &ucirc; zanistiya Ewrop&icirc; ve gir&ecirc;day&icirc;ye,
t&ecirc;bigih&ecirc;jin?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di heman wext&ecirc; de ew pirs&ecirc;n jor&icirc;n dikarin p&ecirc;&thorn;k&ecirc;&thorn;&icirc;
hewldana &thorn;&ecirc;wexwaz a ku em li ser peyiv&icirc;b&ucirc;n,
bibin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ma gelo tazeger&icirc; pirseke gi&thorn;t&icirc; yan j&icirc;
takekes&icirc; ye?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ma gelo tazeger&icirc; bi xwe ne l&ecirc;pirs&icirc;n e? Bi (NA)
y&ecirc; bersivdana van pirsan ne d&icirc;tin &ucirc; nepejirandina
y&ecirc;n d&icirc;tir e, wek ku Edon&icirc;s dib&ecirc;je neb&ucirc;na
azad&icirc; &ucirc; guft&ucirc;goy&ecirc; ye &ucirc; t&ecirc;negihi&thorn;tina
tazegeriy&ecirc; bi xwe ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Qirkirin &ucirc; bindestkirin &ucirc; nepejirandina bawer&icirc;
&ucirc; raman&ecirc;n &ecirc;n d&icirc;tir, an j&icirc; &thorn;&ecirc;weyek&icirc;
amade &ucirc; diyar bo d&icirc;tina tazeger&icirc; &ucirc; xwendina
c&icirc;han&ecirc;, bixwe; serj&ecirc;kirin &ucirc; gurandin &ucirc;
qurmi&ccedil;andina tazegeriy&ecirc; ye, t&ecirc;gihi&thorn;tineke
&ccedil;ar&ccedil;ewekir&icirc; ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Digel v&ecirc; j&icirc;, peydakirin &ucirc; &ccedil;&ecirc;kirina
formeke d&icirc;tir di &ccedil;e&thorn;n&ecirc; forma ber&ecirc;
de ya ku li ser w&ecirc;je &ucirc; &ccedil;anda &ccedil;&icirc;nan
&ucirc; neynika civatan dipeyiv&icirc;, eyn&icirc; serencam e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Tazeger&icirc; di &ccedil;i babet&ecirc; de be, dixwaze asteke
ciwan &ucirc; k&ucirc;r &ucirc; vekir&icirc; ava bike. Dixwaze
pencereyek&ecirc; di d&icirc;war&ecirc; b&ecirc;bizav &ucirc;
b&ecirc;deng de; di d&icirc;war&ecirc; aniha de bo d&icirc;tina
rex&ecirc; d&icirc;tir ji dunyay&ecirc;, veke. Wisa, li dij&icirc;
hem&icirc; form&ecirc;n &ccedil;&ecirc;kir&icirc; &ucirc; amadekir&icirc;
radiweste.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
R. Part li ser aferandin&ecirc; wisa dib&ecirc;je: &quot;afirandin
an &ccedil;&ecirc;kirin, bo c&icirc;han&ecirc; n&ecirc;r&icirc;neke
resen e, xema afirandin&ecirc; afirandina c&icirc;haneke rasteq&icirc;n
e; di form&ecirc; c&icirc;hana yekem de, ne ku ji bo w&ecirc;
c&icirc;han&ecirc; bi w&ecirc;ne bike l&ecirc; da ku w&ecirc;
nemir bike&quot;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi v&icirc; away&icirc; pev&ccedil;&ucirc;na tazegeriy&ecirc;
ji nava xwe &ucirc; ji dervey&icirc; xwe dest p&ecirc; dike. Pencereyek
e bo hejandina d&icirc;rok&ecirc; &ucirc; bi al&icirc;kariya guman&ecirc;
rehayiyan (mutleqan) sist dike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Wek ku &ccedil;awan &icirc;ro j&icirc; ji bo p&ecirc;&thorn;eroj&ecirc;
mirov dipirse; Ramboud di wexta xwe de pirs&icirc; b&ucirc;: &quot;ji
bo &ccedil;i em diniv&icirc;s&icirc;nin eger ne ji bo guhertina
jiyana me be, ku ne ji bo naskirina c&icirc;hanek&ecirc; ku ew
c&icirc;han bi xwe ne c&icirc;hana me ya rast&icirc;n be?&quot;
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Tazeger di &ccedil;ar&ccedil;ewa awez (aqil) &ucirc; alav&ecirc;n
k&ucirc;r &ucirc; berfireh de; t&ecirc;ramandin e. Ew t&ecirc;ramandin
j&icirc; berhemdariya &ccedil;andeke zanist&icirc; ye ku li ser
t&ecirc;k&ccedil;&ucirc;na &ccedil;andeke kevnare ji dayik dibe.
Herwisa t&ecirc;ramandina tazeger&icirc;yane hem&icirc; b&icirc;r&ucirc;baweriy&ecirc;n
sade &ucirc; remak&icirc; (fitr&icirc;) dileriz&icirc;ne; dihej&icirc;ne,
dideriz&icirc;ne &ucirc; diherif&icirc;ne. Lewra tazeger&icirc;
li hember&icirc; w&ecirc; p&ecirc;vajoya ku li ser bingeha bersivdan&ecirc;
ava dibe, radiweste, hewl dide ku p&ecirc;vajoya t&ecirc;ramandina
lihevhat&icirc; &ucirc; gunc&icirc;nam&ecirc;z bi t&ecirc;ramandineke
nakokiyane &ucirc; cih&ecirc; reng; gumanhilgir &ucirc; vekir&icirc;,
biguher&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ango, tazeger&icirc; ji ber xwe ve ji dayik nabe, &ccedil;ink&icirc;
tazeger&icirc; serencama proseseke d&ucirc;r &ucirc; dir&ecirc;j
e; proseseke d&icirc;rok&icirc;, komelayet&icirc;, abor&icirc;,
zanist&icirc; &ucirc; &thorn;aristan&icirc; &ucirc; ps&icirc;koloj&icirc;
ye; la&thorn;&ecirc; f&icirc;z&icirc;k&icirc; y&ecirc; berhemdariya
civat&ecirc; ye. Ji bo p&ecirc;wistiy&ecirc;n d&icirc;rok&icirc;
&ucirc; ji &ccedil;esipandina ziman&ecirc; ku civat diafir&icirc;ne,
n&icirc;&thorn;ana guhertineke diyal&icirc;kt&icirc;k&icirc; ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ew proses j&icirc; yekal&icirc; &ucirc; yekast n&icirc;ne, ji
ber ku di &ccedil;ar&ccedil;ewa wan xal&ecirc;n ku em li ser rawestiyab&ucirc;n
guhertineke &ccedil;away&icirc;n&icirc; berfireh &ucirc; k&ucirc;r
e. Ev guhertin bi xwe j&icirc; awezek&icirc; (aqilek&icirc;) n&ucirc;
dirust dike; ev awez j&icirc; zimanek&icirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;rane
y&icirc; zanistiyane radigih&icirc;ne, ev ziman&ecirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;rane
j&icirc;; neagah&icirc; &ucirc; hest&ecirc;n bi civat&ecirc;;
bi agahiyeke komelane &ucirc; takekesane, diguher&icirc;ne. Bi
wateyeke d&icirc; tazeger&icirc;, &icirc;ro, rexnel&ecirc;girtin
&ucirc; xwendin &ucirc; berhemkirina d&icirc;rok&ecirc; ye, li
ser bingeha ziman&ecirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc; ava dibe.
Pi&thorn;tre w&ecirc; d&icirc;rok&ecirc; bo &icirc;ro diguh&ecirc;z&icirc;ne
(ji n&ucirc; ve durustkirina xwe ya xwe ye &ucirc; c&icirc;hana
me ya windakir&icirc; ye).
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; gelo, hi&thorn;mendiya civata me &ucirc; awira v&ecirc;
civat&ecirc; ya li ser gerd&ucirc;n &ucirc; jiyan&ecirc;, dikar&icirc;b&ucirc;n,
wan guhertin&ecirc;n ku em li ser peyiv&icirc;b&ucirc;n, himb&ecirc;z
bikin; daku pirs&ecirc;n suryal&icirc;zm&ecirc; &ucirc; strakt&ucirc;ralizm&ecirc;
&ucirc; gotara awez (x&icirc;taba aqil) ligel pirs&ecirc;n me
&ucirc; gotara awez&ecirc; me, biguncin, &ucirc; di w&ecirc; sewiyet&ecirc;
de bin?.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ma gelo &ccedil;anda me dikar&icirc;b&ucirc; deqine (t&ecirc;kstine)
di &ccedil;e&thorn;n&ecirc; deq&ecirc;n Jims Jowis &ucirc; Gote
&ucirc; Holdren &ucirc; Briton &ucirc; Tzara &ucirc; Bodl&ecirc;r
&ucirc; Brost, biafir&icirc;ne; daku em wan deqan bi gotara awez
bixw&icirc;nin?.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ica b&icirc;r &ucirc; bawer&icirc; &ucirc; r&ecirc;baz&ecirc;n
teor&icirc; y&ecirc;n ku li Ewrupay&ecirc; peyda dibin, di war&ecirc;
rexnegir&icirc; &ucirc; xwendin &ucirc; anal&icirc;ziya sosyolog&icirc;
&ucirc; ipst&icirc;molog&icirc; &ucirc; f&icirc;lolog&icirc; &ucirc;
ps&icirc;kolog&icirc; &ucirc; zanistiya d&icirc;rok&icirc; de;
r&ecirc;bazine giran in; &ucirc; wan bixwe avahiya abor&icirc;
ya kap&icirc;tal&icirc;zm&ecirc; durust kirin e. Di v&ecirc; avahiy&ecirc;
de, gotara zim&ecirc;n roleke bingeh&icirc;n dil&icirc;ze.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi herhal, tazeger&icirc; wan b&ucirc;yeran &ucirc; wan nim&ucirc;nedaran;
&ucirc; deq&ecirc;n pa&thorn;eroj&ecirc; ber bi afsan &ucirc;
ziman&ecirc; &icirc;ro de radiki&thorn;&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Er&ecirc; &icirc;ro em di c&icirc;hana xwe de p&ecirc;rg&icirc;
deq &ucirc; nim&ucirc;ne &ucirc; &thorn;&ecirc;we &ucirc; diyardey&ecirc;n
di &ccedil;ar&ccedil;eweke &ccedil;andey&icirc; y&icirc; n&ucirc;jen;
taze &ucirc; p&ecirc;&thorn;ve&ccedil;&ucirc;y&icirc;, nabin.
Ne j&icirc; em p&ecirc;rg&icirc; helbesteke n&ucirc;jen, pex&thorn;aneke
n&ucirc;jen &ucirc; romaneke n&ucirc;jen dibin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Tazegeriya Ewrupay&ecirc; ya bilez &ucirc; aloz, b&ucirc;ye sedema
ku em berhem&ecirc;n &ccedil;andey&icirc; y&ecirc;n di hinav&ecirc;n
d&icirc;roka xwe de ji b&icirc;r bikin. &Ccedil;ink&icirc; her
&ucirc; her me bi awak&icirc; ne rew&thorn;enb&icirc;rane away&ecirc;
ewrupiyan kiriye. &Ccedil;ink&icirc; di meydana &ccedil;anda me
ya netew&icirc; de hest&ecirc;n bi&thorn;&ucirc;ndemay&icirc;na
me ya d&icirc;rok&icirc;, reh&ecirc;n xwe dajon.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Digel ku &ccedil;avkaniy&ecirc;n rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;
&ucirc; hi&thorn;yariya k&ucirc;r a rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r &ucirc;
hizirvan &ucirc; ramyar &ucirc; dah&ecirc;ner &ucirc; helbestvan&ecirc;n
mezin &ecirc;n Ewrupay&ecirc; sof&icirc;zma rojhilat &ucirc; afsan
&ucirc; kult&ucirc;ra kevnare ya Igr&icirc;kiyan e j&icirc;, rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
kurd &icirc;ro, berevaj&icirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n Ewrupay&ecirc;,
hewl dide ku van aliyan ji b&icirc;r bike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ji bo &ccedil;esipandina v&ecirc; yek&ecirc; j&icirc;, pir k&ecirc;m
li ser ezm&ucirc;neya Goran&ecirc; nemir t&ecirc;t peyiv&icirc;n.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi baweriya min, di meydana rew&thorn;enb&icirc;riya me de; ji
n&icirc;v&ecirc; v&ecirc; sedsal&ecirc; &ucirc; vir de, pirsek
di v&ecirc; sewiyet&ecirc; de, pirsek ku bikaribe derzek&ecirc;
di m&ecirc;jiy&ecirc; me de wek derza ku Goran&icirc; durist kiriye,
li ber &ccedil;av n&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&Ccedil;ink&icirc; ezm&ucirc;neya Goran &thorn;iya ziman&ecirc;
ramandin&ecirc; ji klas&icirc;kiy&ecirc; bo n&ucirc;jeniy&ecirc;
veke, herwisa w&ecirc; ezm&ucirc;ney&ecirc; &thorn;iya &thorn;&ecirc;we
&ucirc; naverokeke t&icirc;r p&ecirc;&thorn;k&ecirc;&thorn;&icirc;
la&thorn;&ecirc; &ccedil;anda me bike. Bi v&ecirc; yek&ecirc;
j&icirc; &thorn;iya p&ecirc;nasa helbest&icirc; &ucirc; &ccedil;anda
me ji devera me ber bi c&icirc;hankirin&ecirc; de raki&thorn;&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Goran&icirc;, bi palpi&thorn;ta xwe y&icirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;
&ucirc; xwemal&icirc;, bi s&ucirc;dwergirtina ji ezm&ucirc;neya
&ccedil;anda dewr&ucirc;ber &ucirc; d&ucirc;rtir, kar&icirc;b&ucirc;ye
berhemeke rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc; y&icirc; &ccedil;andey&icirc;
&ucirc; hemdem &ucirc; ahengane biafir&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Wate, Goran&icirc; bi awira xwe ya taybet&icirc; bingeha rew&thorn;enb&icirc;riyeke
xwemalane damezirand b&ucirc;. Ev rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;
ne bi away&ecirc; kop&icirc;kirina tazegeriya Ewrupiyan a ku pi&thorn;t&icirc;
Goran &ucirc; heta &icirc;ro j&icirc; di nav rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n
me de berdewam dike, p&ecirc;k an&icirc;b&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; Goran wek dah&ecirc;nerek&icirc; rast&icirc;n dikar&icirc;b&ucirc;
ezm&ucirc;neya w&ecirc; tazegeriy&ecirc; rabigih&icirc;ne, ango
Goran&icirc; ew asoya berfireh ji wergirtin&ecirc; bo aferandin
&ucirc; be&thorn;darb&ucirc;n&ecirc; &ccedil;&ecirc;kir.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Goran&icirc; di ezm&ucirc;neya xwe y&icirc; helbest&icirc; de
li teni&thorn;t n&ucirc;kirina zim&ecirc;n &ucirc; gotara xwendin&ecirc;
j&icirc;, dikar&icirc;b&ucirc;, komeke b&icirc;r&ucirc;baweriy&ecirc;n
hemdem &ucirc; xwerist&icirc; p&ecirc;&thorn;k&ecirc;&thorn;&icirc;
semta d&icirc;rok&ecirc; &ucirc; jin&ecirc; &ucirc; xwerist&ecirc;
&ucirc; c&icirc;hana giyan&icirc;, bike.. Lewra ev aliy&ecirc;n
balk&ecirc;&thorn;, navika ezm&ucirc;neya Goran&icirc; bo me bi
c&icirc; dih&ecirc;lin, d&icirc;sa wan aliyan bi xwe j&icirc;
dah&ecirc;nan &ucirc; berdewamkirina ezm&ucirc;neya Goran sist
kirin. 
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Hetan&icirc; roja &icirc;ro j&icirc;, rexnegiriya me ya ku xwe
disp&ecirc;re herd&ucirc; rex&ecirc;n siyas&icirc;; li ser helwest
&ucirc; b&icirc;r&ucirc;baweriy&ecirc;n siyas&icirc; y&ecirc;n
Goran, radiweste, &ucirc; wek asteng l&ecirc; tema&thorn;e dike,
digel ku rexnegiriya me bixwe j&icirc; di heman asteng&ecirc;
de dij&icirc;. Eger em Goran&icirc; bi b&icirc;r&ucirc;baweriy&ecirc;n
w&icirc; y&ecirc;n siyas&icirc; gunehbar &ucirc; rexne dikin,
mane hem&icirc; mamosta &ucirc; serpere&thorn;t &ucirc; n&ucirc;ner&ecirc;n
helbest &ucirc; rexnegiriy&ecirc;, &icirc;ro ro, d&icirc;l&ecirc;n
siyaset&ecirc; ne &ucirc; bi part&icirc;tiya teng hatine merbend
kirin. Ji xwe ev diyarde, di war&ecirc; nasnameya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
me y&icirc; &icirc;ro de, zelaltir&icirc;n diyarde ye. Lewra dixwazim
v&ecirc; yek&ecirc; bi pirsek&ecirc; kuta bikim:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
K&icirc;jan rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd, &icirc;ro ro, nasnameya
xwe ya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;, ji dervey&icirc; &ccedil;ar&ccedil;ewa
siyaseta partiyane, bi dest dix&icirc;ne?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
B&ecirc;guman liserawestan &ucirc; pirsa &ccedil;anda kurd&icirc;
ya li tarawgeh&ecirc; &ucirc; pitsa rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
kurd &ecirc; mi&thorn;ext &ucirc; derbiderb&ucirc;y&icirc;, ji
astenga gi&thorn;t&icirc; ya rew&thorn;a &ccedil;anda me y&icirc;
li hundir&ecirc; wel&ecirc;t, cuda nabe. &Ccedil;ink&icirc; hetan&icirc;
aniha n&ecirc;r&icirc;na gi&thorn;t&icirc; ya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;
ya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd li dervey&icirc; wel&ecirc;t
be&thorn;ek ji &ccedil;anda hundire &ucirc; nikare j&ecirc; cih&ecirc;
bibe ango &thorn;iyan &ucirc; h&ecirc;za &ccedil;anda kurd&icirc;
li derve her ew &thorn;iyan &ucirc; h&ecirc;za &ccedil;anda hundir
e. Bi wateyeke d&icirc;; du jeografiyay&ecirc;n &ccedil;anda kurd&icirc;
n&icirc;n in, digel v&ecirc; j&icirc;, v&ecirc; tarawgeh&ecirc;,
v&ecirc; guhertina cih, gelek deng daqurtandine. Deng&ecirc;n
hey&icirc; ti deng&ecirc;n n&ucirc; dernexistine &ucirc; tarawgeh&ecirc;
j&icirc; dengine d&icirc;tir, neafirandiye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Lewra em li hember&icirc; &ccedil;end&icirc;n sedem &ucirc; hokar&ecirc;n
aloz&icirc; r&ucirc; bi r&ucirc; radiwestin, &ucirc; ji bo ron&icirc;kirina
v&ecirc; yek&ecirc; j&icirc;, b&ecirc;guman, em hewcedar&icirc;
gelek belgeyan in. Digel ku karek&icirc; wisa me na&ccedil;ar
dike ku em vegerin komek &ccedil;avkan&icirc; &ucirc; b&icirc;r&ucirc;baweriy&ecirc;n
ku li ser t&ecirc;rma intil&icirc;g&ecirc;nsya radiwesin. L&ecirc;
mixabin, ne ev l&ecirc;kol&icirc;n dikare v&icirc; bar&icirc;
hilgire &ucirc; ne j&icirc; ez dikarim be&thorn;dar&icirc; v&ecirc;
p&ecirc;diviya zanist&icirc; y&icirc; teor&icirc; bibim. 
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; bi cegerdar&icirc; dikarim bib&ecirc;jim ku berztir&icirc;n
asteng&ecirc;n &ccedil;anda me hejariya t&ecirc;rma kurd a zanist&icirc;
di danas&icirc;na t&ecirc;rma intil&icirc;g&ecirc;nsya de ye..
Ango rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n ku bikaribin, wek p&icirc;&thorn;e,
bi anal&icirc;z&ecirc; &ucirc; bi p&ecirc;&thorn;debirina projeyeke
raman&icirc; &ucirc; felsef&icirc; &ucirc; zanist&icirc; &ucirc;
rexney&icirc; &ucirc; &ccedil;end aliy&ecirc;n d&icirc;tir &ecirc;n
hi&thorn;yar&icirc; &ucirc; w&ecirc;jey&icirc; mij&ucirc;l ,bibin
n&icirc;n in. L&ecirc; em dikarin bib&ecirc;jin ku rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
kurd, wek karek&icirc; rojane, mirovek&icirc; normal e bi her
ti&thorn;t&icirc; mij&ucirc;l dibe yan j&icirc; wek ku p&ecirc;&thorn;iyan
gotiye: ((Ji her baxek&icirc; gulek)).
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Lewra ti r&ecirc;bazeke zanist&icirc; &ucirc; hi&thorn;yar&icirc;
y&icirc; s&icirc;norkir&icirc; bi karnay&icirc;ne, &ucirc; ligel
hem&icirc; cihan j&icirc; digunce.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
B&ecirc;guman gerek ez bib&ecirc;jim ku &ccedil;end rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n
kurd y&ecirc;n xwedan heb&ucirc;neke taybet&icirc;, hetan&icirc;
aniha berhem&ecirc;n wan ne hatine nirxandin &ucirc; ne j&icirc;
l&ecirc;kol&icirc;n&ecirc;n balk&ecirc;&thorn; li ser wan berheman
rawestiyane.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Biherhal, aloztir&icirc;n d&icirc;men ew e ku ti cudah&icirc;
di navbera rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n derve &ucirc; hundir
de n&icirc;n e. Ji xwe lawaziya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd
&ecirc; li dervey&icirc; wel&ecirc;t ji pa&thorn;eroja w&icirc;
t&ecirc;t, &ccedil;ink&icirc; ew bixwe bi &ccedil;andeke gi&thorn;t&icirc;
hatiye perwerdekirin, ku bi w&ecirc; &ccedil;and&ecirc;, di serencama
daw&icirc; de, li dervey&icirc; wel&ecirc;t, nikare li ser bingeh&ecirc;n
tund bixebite.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Mijar&ecirc;n ku li Kurdistan&ecirc; li ser zim&ecirc;n b&ucirc;n,
li vir, li tarawgeh&ecirc;, b&ecirc; zem&icirc;n &ucirc; b&ecirc;
xwendevan in.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Herwisa, t&ecirc;gihi&thorn;tina rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
me &ucirc; asoy&ecirc;n hi&thorn;yariya w&icirc;, li vir, li dervey&icirc;
wel&ecirc;t, li beramber&icirc; v&ecirc; tabloya tevl&icirc;hev
&ucirc; k&ucirc;r a tiknolojya &ucirc; &thorn;aristaniy&ecirc;,
hi&thorn;tine ku r&ucirc; bi r&ucirc; li hember pirseke &ccedil;andey&icirc;
cih&ecirc;reng raweste, ku rew&thorn;enb&icirc;rek&icirc; di &ccedil;e&thorn;n&ecirc;
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd de ti car&icirc; nikare bersiva
w&ecirc; pirs&ecirc; wergire &ucirc; bi destx&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Digel v&ecirc; j&icirc;, sist&ecirc;m &ucirc; form&ecirc;n jiyan&ecirc;
y&ecirc;n tevl&icirc;hev &ecirc;n welat&ecirc;n tarawgwh&ecirc;,
bi hem&icirc; movik &ucirc; &thorn;ax&ecirc;n xwe; jiyana ku li
ser program &ucirc; dabe&thorn;kirina dem&ecirc; ava dibe &ucirc;
li p&ecirc;diviy&ecirc;n jiyana rojane digere, wek jiyaneke n&ucirc;
ligel s&icirc;st&ecirc;ma b&ecirc; program a rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
kurd &ecirc; li dervey&icirc; wel&ecirc;t, nagunce. Lewra, v&ecirc;
rew&thorn;&ecirc;, rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me vegerandiye
destp&ecirc;keke d&icirc;tir ku ji destp&ecirc;ka p&ecirc;&thorn;&icirc;n
bi hem&icirc; away&ecirc;n xwe cih&ecirc;reng e, &ucirc; ew ji
xwendin&ecirc; bi d&ucirc;rxistiye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Li teni&thorn;t v&ecirc;, alav&ecirc;n ragihandin&ecirc; (Televizyon,
rojnameger&icirc;, &ccedil;alakiy&ecirc;n li ser kolanan, aheng
&ucirc; &thorn;ev&ecirc;n &thorn;ahiy&ecirc; &ucirc; h d) giyan&ecirc;
v&icirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; ku h&icirc;n&icirc; jiyaneke
wisa neb&ucirc;ye, vala kiriye, zuha kiriye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ev &ucirc; &ccedil;end hokar&ecirc;n d&icirc;tir, bi taybet&icirc;
avahiya me ya rojhilat&icirc;, me di hundir&ecirc; v&ecirc; jeografiya
n&ucirc; de ber bi tenhat&icirc; &ucirc; li xwep&ecirc;&ccedil;an&ecirc;
de, dehf dane.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
B&ecirc;guman mebesta min rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd &ecirc;
li Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc; ye y&ecirc; ku dikare bibe nim&ucirc;neyeke
gi&thorn;t&icirc; bo rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n kurd &ecirc;n
li dervey&icirc; wel&ecirc;t.. Digel ku navendey&ecirc;n &ccedil;and&icirc;,
&ccedil;apxane &ucirc; kovar &ucirc; Radyo &ucirc; &ccedil;alakiy&ecirc;n
&ccedil;and&icirc; &ucirc; huner&icirc; y&ecirc;n ku li Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc;
peyda dibin li ti welatek&icirc; Ewropay&ecirc; peyda nabin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&Icirc;ca ligor sewiyeta v&ecirc; &ccedil;anda ku li Kurdistana
Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc; li ber dest e em dikarin s&icirc;nor&ecirc;n
&ccedil;anda xwe ya li dervey&icirc; wel&ecirc;t destn&icirc;&thorn;an
bikin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez dib&ecirc;jim Kurdistana Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc; &ccedil;ink&icirc;
&icirc;ro ro wek hejmara van navend&ecirc;n sexte &ucirc; van
komeley&ecirc;n b&ecirc;encam li kurdistana ku welat e n&icirc;n
in.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di &ccedil;avkaniyeke Sw&ecirc;d&icirc; de ku li ser berhem&ecirc;n
&ccedil;apb&ucirc;y&icirc; y&ecirc;n sala 1994 an &ecirc;n bi
ziman&ecirc;n hem&icirc; penaber&ecirc;n li Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc;,
hetine &ccedil;apkirin, dipeyive, wisa dib&ecirc;je: ((Kurd ji
hem&icirc; gel&ecirc;n d&icirc;tir b&ecirc;tir xwedan&ecirc;n
navend&ecirc;n &ccedil;ap&ecirc; &ucirc; malbend&ecirc;n &ccedil;and&icirc;
ne, &ucirc; ji hemiyan b&ecirc;tir j&icirc; pirt&ucirc;kan diwe&thorn;&icirc;nin)).
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di heman wext&ecirc; de; div&ecirc; b&ecirc; gotin, ku rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;
kurd ji bo berjewendiy&ecirc;n xwe y&ecirc;n abor&icirc; &ucirc;
propogandey&icirc; ji hem&icirc; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n
milet&ecirc;n ku li Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc; dij&icirc;n; sergermtir
e; sergermtir e da ku bibe endam&ecirc; yek&icirc;tiya niv&icirc;skar&ecirc;n
Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc;, ev yek&icirc;tiya ku li vir, li Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc;,
di sewiyeta komeleyeke civak&icirc; de ye, &ucirc; ti rola w&ecirc;
y&icirc; taybet&icirc; di avakirina &ccedil;andeke balk&ecirc;&thorn;
de n&icirc;n e. Ya ji v&ecirc; balk&ecirc;&thorn;tir ew e ku hin
ji endam&ecirc;n yek&icirc;tiya niv&icirc;skar&ecirc;n Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc;
y&ecirc;n kurd di nav rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n kurdan de
bixwe wek niv&icirc;skarine kurd nay&ecirc;n naskirin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Biherhal, dah&ecirc;nan bixwe negunc&icirc;na ligel jiyan&ecirc;
&ucirc; gerd&ucirc;n &ucirc; rew&thorn;a b&ecirc;ango (b&ecirc;
me`ne) ya jiyana rojane ye; negunc&icirc;na ligel real&icirc;tey&ecirc;
ye; real&icirc;teya ku ji al&icirc; deshilat&ecirc; &ucirc; yasay&ecirc;
(qan&ucirc;n&ecirc;) bi bersiv&ecirc;n xwe y&icirc; hi&thorn;k
hatiye &ccedil;&ecirc;kirin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ango aferandin p&ecirc;&thorn;k&ecirc;&thorn;kirina pirseke k&ucirc;r
e; bi heb&ucirc;na mirov&ecirc; dah&ecirc;ner dagirt&icirc;ye,;
dah&ecirc;ner&ecirc; ku di hundir&ecirc; proseseke aloz de dikare,
di hundir&ecirc; xwe de aferandin&ecirc; bi karb&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Lewra mirov&ecirc; dah&ecirc;ner nakokiy&ecirc; hem bi xwe re
&ucirc; hem j&icirc; bi rew&thorn;a xwe y&icirc; civak&icirc;
re, dij&icirc;, &ucirc; bi v&ecirc; qonaxa d&ucirc;r &ucirc; dir&ecirc;j
a jiyan&ecirc; &ucirc; d&icirc;rok&ecirc; re, dij&icirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi xeyala xwe, bi xewna xwe y&icirc; resen &ucirc; gerd&ucirc;n&icirc;;
ji destp&ecirc;k&ecirc; ve; hewl dide ku v&ecirc; c&icirc;hana
ferzb&ucirc;y&icirc;, di hundir&ecirc; meydana deq &ucirc; niv&icirc;s&ecirc;n
xwe de, biherif&icirc;ne, &ucirc; di &thorn;&ucirc;na w&ecirc;
de jiyaneke giyan&icirc; y&icirc; hestdar &ucirc; nemir &ucirc;
mehal, ava bike, bih&ucirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Lewra gerek tarawgeh&ecirc; rew&thorn;eke al&icirc;kar bi dest&ecirc;
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me xista da ku ji real&icirc;tey&ecirc;
cih&ecirc; bibe, l&ecirc; berevaj&icirc; w&ecirc;, &ccedil;ink&icirc;
avahiya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd li ser palpi&thorn;teke
zikmakane &ucirc; li ser bersivdan&ecirc; &ucirc; li ser gunc&icirc;na
ligel gotara serke&thorn;(seth&icirc;) a civak&icirc; &ucirc;
real&icirc;teya berdest, hatiye damezirandin, ti car&icirc; nikare
ne ji civat&ecirc; namo(ixt&icirc;rab) bibe &ucirc; ne j&icirc;
j&ecirc; cuda bibe.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ji ber ku di v&ecirc; jeografiyay&ecirc; &ucirc; di v&icirc; cih&ecirc;
n&ucirc; de; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd bixwe asteng &ucirc;
&ccedil;eper dan&icirc;ne p&ecirc;&thorn;iya xwe da ku xwe ji
ber pirs&ecirc;n tevl&icirc;hev &ecirc;n v&ecirc; jeografyay&ecirc;
ve&thorn;&ecirc;re.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ango hewl dide ku bi &ccedil;av&ecirc;n asayiy&ecirc; (normaliy&ecirc;)
li hem&icirc; ti&thorn;t&ecirc;n seyr &ucirc; biyan, tema&thorn;e
bike da ku her &ucirc; her w&ecirc; gotara (x&icirc;taba) ron
&ucirc; serke&thorn; bipar&ecirc;ze.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Lewra, gotara rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me, bi gi&thorn;t&icirc;,
li tarawgeh&ecirc;, ne&thorn;iyaye gotarek gumanhilgir &ucirc;
balk&ecirc;&thorn; biafir&icirc;ne da ku hem&icirc; &thorn;&ecirc;we
&ucirc; taybetiy&ecirc;n ku tarawgeh&ecirc; dinas&icirc;nin, bikarb&icirc;ne.
Da ku niv&icirc;sandina xwe berdewam bike, her &ucirc; her hewl
dide ku alav &ucirc; &thorn;&ecirc;wey&ecirc;n xwe y&ecirc;n kevnare
di b&icirc;ra xwe de vej&icirc;ne da ku bi pa&thorn;eroja xwe
re &ucirc; bi peywendiy&ecirc;n w&ecirc; pa&thorn;eroj&ecirc;
re berdewam bibe. Wisa rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me baweriyeke
nehi&thorn;yariyane dirust dike da ku pi&thorn;ta xwe bide hem&icirc;
pirs&ecirc;n v&ecirc; jeografyay&ecirc;. Ango bi bahaney&ecirc;n
rew&thorn;a Kurdistan&ecirc; &ucirc; bi d&ucirc;rb&ucirc;na ji
wel&ecirc;t &ucirc; b&ucirc;yeran, derfeta avakirina xwe ji dest
winda dike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ji al&icirc;k&icirc; din ve; zem&icirc;na abor&icirc; ya ku li
tarawgeh&ecirc; peyda dibe &ucirc; bi taybet&icirc; li Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc;;
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd dehf daye ku &ccedil;and &ucirc;
peyva kurd&icirc; wek alaveke bazirgan&icirc; bi karb&icirc;ne,
v&ecirc; yek&ecirc; bixwe j&icirc; d&icirc;men&ecirc;n &ccedil;anda
me, li tarawgeh&ecirc;, zel&ucirc;ltir &ucirc; hejartir, kirinye..
&Ccedil;ink&icirc; v&ecirc; diyardeya malkambax bixwe hi&thorn;tiye
ku rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; kurd li Siw&ecirc;d&ecirc; rew&thorn;eke
&ccedil;andey&icirc; y&icirc; sext &ucirc; t&ecirc;k&ccedil;&ucirc;y&icirc;
&ucirc; berav&ecirc;t&icirc; p&ecirc;&thorn;k&ecirc;&thorn; bike,
nehi&thorn;tiye ku rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me bi awak&icirc;
normal &ucirc; bi berdewamiyeke dah&ecirc;nane bij&icirc;; ne
bi xwe re digunce &ucirc; ne j&icirc; bi rew&thorn;a dervey&icirc;
wel&ecirc;t re.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi gotineke din, v&ecirc; zem&icirc;na abor&icirc; wek dadgeh&ecirc;,
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; me, li p&ecirc;&thorn;iya &ccedil;av&ecirc;n
me r&ucirc;tkiriye; rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc; ku ne dikare
bixw&icirc;ne &ucirc; ne j&icirc; dikare li ser bingeheke taybet&icirc;
xwe ava bike; &ucirc; ne j&icirc; dikare pirsan &ucirc; deqek&icirc;
rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;; hi&thorn;mend&icirc;, &ucirc; ebediyane,
biafir&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Lewra, di meydana &ccedil;and &ucirc; peyva kurd&icirc; ya ku
li dervey&icirc; wel&ecirc;t hatiye niv&icirc;sandin; hetan&icirc;
aniha; pirseke rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc; y&icirc; cih&ecirc;reng,
hem ku ji pirs&ecirc;n hundir&ecirc; wel&ecirc;t cih&ecirc; be
&ucirc; hem j&icirc; ku bikaribe sewi-yeta &ccedil;anda me ya
gi&thorn;t&icirc; biliv&icirc;ne, n&icirc;n e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Berevaj&icirc; w&ecirc;, &icirc;ro, li wel&ecirc;t, hewldan &ucirc;
bizav&ecirc;n rew&thorn;enb&icirc;ran bo p&ecirc;kan&icirc;na
guhertinek&ecirc;, hem &ccedil;alaktir &ucirc; hem j&icirc; xurtir
in.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Jixwe rexne &ucirc; liserawestaneke anal&icirc;zane y&icirc; balk&ecirc;&thorn;;
li vir, ku pirs&ecirc;n bingeh&icirc;n &ecirc;n &ccedil;anda me
ne; &icirc;ro ro, n&icirc;n in.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi kurt&icirc;, di baweriya min de, hetan&icirc; v&ecirc; k&ecirc;l&icirc;k&ecirc;,
gotara rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc; ya tarawgeh&ecirc;, meydana
d&icirc;dariya rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&ecirc;n kurd di war&ecirc;
form &ucirc; naverok&ecirc; de, ji wan alav&ecirc;n ku ji wel&ecirc;t
bi xwe re an&icirc;ne, p&ecirc;k t&ecirc;. Ango, gotara rew&thorn;enb&icirc;r&icirc;
ya tarawgeh&ecirc; ne ji prosesa namob&ucirc;n&ecirc; (ixt&icirc;rab&ecirc;)
ji dayik b&ucirc;ye. l&ecirc;bel&ecirc; ligel v&ecirc; jeografiyay&ecirc;
di namob&ucirc;n &ucirc; tenhat&icirc; negunc&icirc;n&ecirc; de
ye. B&ucirc;da dib&ecirc;je:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
((Guman &ccedil;avkaniya hem&icirc; destp&ecirc;kirinan e... Neman
bo w&icirc; kes&ecirc; ku sefera xwe li ser zem&icirc;n&ecirc;
rawestand... &Ucirc; li de&thorn;t&ecirc; &ccedil;arm&ecirc;rk&icirc;
r&ucirc;ni&thorn;t... Ey dah&ecirc;nerno! H&ucirc;n li k&ucirc;
ne? Ew peyv&ecirc;n ku tu dib&ecirc;j&icirc;; ((hem&icirc; ti&thorn;t
winda b&ucirc;n)), berhema w&icirc; di&ccedil;e nav dil &ucirc;
awez&ecirc;(aqil&ecirc;) me.. Em j&icirc; h&ecirc; ciwan in))
</BLOCKQUOTE>
</BODY>
</HTML>
