<HTML>
<HEAD>
<META HTTP-EQUIV="Content-Type" CONTENT="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1">
<TITLE>NIRXANDINA EDEBIYAT</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.03z">
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<HR>
<H2><CENTER><FONT SIZE=6>NIRXANDINA EDEBIYAT&Ecirc;<BR>
</FONT><FONT SIZE=4>Lokman POLAT <BR>
</FONT></CENTER></H2>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Beriya 1980&icirc; berhem&ecirc;n edeb&icirc; y&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc;
k&ecirc;m b&ucirc;. Niv&icirc;s&ecirc;n li ser edebiyata Kurd&icirc;
pirr k&ecirc;m -car carna- dihatin we&#136;sandin&ecirc;. L&ecirc;
pi&#136;st&icirc; 1980'y&icirc; &ucirc; bi taybet&icirc; j&icirc;
di sal&ecirc;n nabeyna 1985 &ucirc; 1995an de gelek berhem&ecirc;n
edeb&icirc; -li wel&ecirc;t &ucirc; li dervey&ecirc; wel&ecirc;t-
hatin afirandin, bi sedan niv&icirc;s&ecirc;n li ser bi gelemper&icirc;
edebiyat&ecirc; &ucirc; bi taybet&icirc; j&icirc; edebiyata Kurd&icirc;
hatin we&#136;sandin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ziman, &ccedil;and &ucirc; edebiyata neteweyek heb&ucirc;na w&ecirc;
netewey&icirc; ye. Neteweyek ku ziman&ecirc; xwe, &ccedil;anda
xwe, edebiyata xwe wenda bike, ew bi xwe j&icirc; wenda dibe,
di nav netewey&ecirc;n din de dihele, as&icirc;m&icirc;le dibe.
Y&ecirc;n ku neteweyan li ser lingan dih&ecirc;le ziman, &ccedil;and
&ucirc; edebiyata w&icirc; netewey&icirc; ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Edebiyata Kurd&icirc; a bi devk&icirc; gelek xurt e, dewlemend
e. Edebiyata niv&icirc;sk&icirc; ze&icirc;fe, l&ecirc; di van
sal&ecirc;n daw&icirc;n de, edebiyata niv&icirc;sk&icirc; j&icirc;
ber bi p&ecirc;&#136;s dikeve, p&ecirc;&#136;sve di&ccedil;e,
dewlemend dibe.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Edebiyat di jiyana gel &ucirc; neteweyan de b&ucirc;yer&ecirc;n
ku li ser jiyana civak&icirc; bandora xwe dike, bi hawayek&icirc;
hizn, hest &ucirc; bi s&icirc;mgeyan, bi tasw&icirc;ran, bi gotinan
yan j&icirc; bi niv&icirc;sk&icirc; t&ecirc;te p&ecirc;&#136;sk&ecirc;&#136;skirin.
Di edebiyat&ecirc; de ziman bingeh e; ziman nebe edebiyat nabe.
L&ecirc;, dewlemendiya zim&ecirc;n j&icirc; bi t&ecirc;kiliy&ecirc;n
bi edebiyat&ecirc; ve gir&ecirc;day&icirc; ye. Bi karan&icirc;na
ziman&ecirc; edeb&icirc;, ew ziman h&icirc;n p&ecirc;&#136;s dikeve,
bi go&#136;st &ucirc; xw&icirc;n dibe, bi ruh &ucirc; can dibe,
j&icirc;ndar dibe. P&ecirc;&#136;s ve di&ccedil;e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Y&ecirc;n ku di berhem&ecirc;n edeb&icirc; de ziman bi hostat&icirc;
bi kar t&icirc;ne &ucirc; bi zimanek&icirc; dewlemend b&ucirc;yeran
li hev dihone, niv&icirc;skar&ecirc;/a berhem&ecirc;n edeb&icirc;
bi xwe ye. Niv&icirc;skar&ecirc;n berhem&ecirc;n edeb&icirc; di
her dem&icirc; de, bi kultur &ucirc; zanyariya xwe zanay&ecirc;n
dema xwe ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di hem&ucirc; berhem&ecirc;n edeb&icirc; de tezek heye, mesajek
heye. K&icirc; dikare bib&ecirc;je ku berhema nemir ya netewa
Kurd, Mem &ucirc; Z&icirc;n b&ecirc; mesaj e, b&ecirc;tez e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&Ccedil;alakiy&ecirc;n edeb&icirc; bi afirandina berhem&ecirc;n
edeb&icirc; xwe dide xuyakirin. Di her dem&icirc; de y&ecirc;n
ku bi h&ecirc;z&ecirc;n tar&icirc; re &#136;ser dikin, t&ecirc;diko&#136;sin
rew&#136;senb&icirc;r &ucirc; hunermend&ecirc;n p&ecirc;&#136;sver&ucirc;
ne. Di v&ecirc; t&ecirc;ko&#136;s&icirc;n&ecirc; de, di gelek
welatan de bi sedan niv&icirc;skar &ucirc; rew&#136;senb&icirc;r
dikevin z&icirc;ndanan, hinek&ecirc;n wan j&icirc; t&ecirc;ne
ku&#136;stin&ecirc;. Berhem &ucirc; jiyana wan niv&icirc;skaran
ji nesl&ecirc;n dahat&ucirc; re, ji p&ecirc;&#136;seroj&ecirc;
re dibe m&icirc;nak.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di nirxandina edebiyat&ecirc; de ti&#136;st&ecirc; her&icirc;
bi xeter sektar&icirc;zm e. Sektar&icirc;zm &#136;s&ecirc;weyek&icirc;
nihil&icirc;zm&ecirc; ye. Hem&ucirc; ti&#136;st&ecirc;n ber&ecirc;
&icirc;nkar dike &ucirc; dixwaze d&icirc;tin&ecirc;n xwe bi zor&ecirc;
bide qeb&ucirc;lkirin. Rasteq&icirc;n&icirc; bi &icirc;nkar&ecirc;
dernakeve hol&ecirc;. Rasteq&icirc;n&icirc; bi yek&icirc;tiya
nakokiyan t&ecirc; f&ecirc;mkirin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Doxmat&icirc;zm li p&ecirc;&#136;sber&ecirc; p&ecirc;&#136;sve&ccedil;&ucirc;na
edebiyat&ecirc; asteng e. Di doxmat&icirc;zm&ecirc; de guhartin
&ucirc; xwen&ucirc;hkirin t&ucirc;ne ye. Kes&ecirc;n doxmat&icirc;k
di nav l&ecirc;ger&icirc;n&ecirc; de n&icirc;nin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di edebiyat&ecirc; de ala her&icirc; ber bi p&ecirc;&#136;s real&icirc;zma
modern e. Real&icirc;zma n&ucirc;jen yek al&icirc; n&icirc;ne,
pas&icirc;f n&icirc;ne, akt&icirc;f e, bi tes&icirc;re, f&ecirc;r
dike. Real&icirc;zma n&ucirc;jen xwe ji doxmat&icirc;zm&ecirc;
&ucirc; demagojiy&ecirc; dipar&ecirc;ze. Real&icirc;zma n&ucirc;jen,
ba&#136;siy&ecirc;, rindiy&ecirc;, bedewiy&ecirc; derdixe p&ecirc;&#136;s.
Ew her tim h&ecirc;viy&ecirc; dij&icirc;ne. Di edebiyat&ecirc;
de real&icirc;zm, b&ucirc;yer&ecirc;, mewziy&ecirc;, wak&icirc;ay&ecirc;
wek xwe, di nav herikandina b&ucirc;yer&ecirc; de day&icirc;n
e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Hinek berhem&ecirc;n edeb&icirc; hene, ku ji bo mirov&ecirc;n
di dema xwe de hatine niv&icirc;sandin. L&ecirc;, ev berhem&ecirc;n
nemir him ji bo w&ecirc; dem&ecirc;, him ji bo dema me &ucirc;
him j&icirc; ji bo dema p&ecirc;&#136;seroj&ecirc; j&icirc; berhem&ecirc;n
edeb&icirc; ne. Mem &ucirc; Z&icirc;n, Don K&icirc;&#136;sot,
&THORN;er &ucirc; A&#136;s&icirc;t&icirc; &ucirc; hwd, berhem&ecirc;n
weha ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Edebiyat; ji helbest&ecirc; hetan&icirc; &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;,
ji dastan &ucirc; menq&icirc;bey&ecirc;n ol&icirc; hetan&icirc;
roman&ecirc; t&ecirc;t avakirin. Ev hem&ucirc; &#136;sax&ecirc;n
edebiyat&ecirc; bi hevdu ve gir&ecirc;day&icirc;ne &ucirc; bingeha
wan li ser hunera &ccedil;&icirc;rokkirin&ecirc; -h&icirc;kayekirin&ecirc;-
ava dibe. Helbest j&icirc;, roman j&icirc;, &THORN;ano-tiyatro-
j&icirc;, senaryo j&icirc;, h&icirc;kayetkirin e -&ccedil;&icirc;rokkirin
e. Ji xwe hunera edeb&icirc;, qalkirin e, h&icirc;kayekirin e.
Cudah&icirc;buy&icirc;na wan di tekn&icirc;ka h&icirc;kayekirin&ecirc;
de ye. Edebiyat biriqandina -yansitma- jiyana j&icirc;ndaran e.
Di edebiyat&ecirc; de t&icirc;p &ucirc; qarekter c&icirc;hek&icirc;
gir&icirc;ng digire.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di nav &#136;sax&ecirc;n edebiyat&ecirc; de ya her&icirc; kevn
helbest e. Helbest wek nes&icirc;r d&ucirc;z n&icirc;ne. Bi p&icirc;van
e, bi wezn e. Helbest b&ucirc;ne kilam &ucirc; stran, bi muz&icirc;k&ecirc;
hatine xwendin &ucirc; gotin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Roman h&ecirc;j n&ucirc;h e. S&ecirc; asir ber&ecirc; hatiye avakirin.
Di esra 18 &ucirc; 19an de gih&icirc;&#136;stiye kemala xwe. Roman
h&ecirc;j j&icirc; ber bi p&ecirc;&#136;s ve di&ccedil;e, bi tekn&icirc;k&ecirc;n
n&ucirc;h dikemile. Di romanan de t&ecirc;kiliy&ecirc;n mirovan
-&icirc;nsanan- y&ecirc;n bi hevdu re &ucirc; bi xwezayiy&ecirc;
re bi hawak&icirc; berfireh &ucirc; bi teferuat t&ecirc;t qalkirin,
bi huner&icirc; t&ecirc; h&icirc;kayekirin. Di nav van t&ecirc;kiliyan
de; ji pirs&ecirc;n ruh&icirc; hetan&icirc; rew&#136;sa abor&icirc;
&ucirc; gelek munasebet&ecirc;n din hene. Di h&icirc;kayekirina
ev&icirc;ndariya du ciwanan de munasebeta civak&icirc; ya w&ecirc;
dever&ecirc;, w&ecirc; herem&ecirc; heye. Roman vekirin &ucirc;
derketina hol&ecirc; ya munasebeta civak&icirc; ye. Roman ke&#136;sifek&icirc;
n&ucirc;h e, &icirc;catek&icirc; n&ucirc; ye. Tekn&icirc;ka avakirina
w&ecirc; tim t&ecirc; guherandin, t&ecirc; n&ucirc;hkirin. Firqa
di navbera roman &ucirc; &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; de n&icirc;cel
n&icirc;n e, n&icirc;tel e, wesf e. Her&ccedil;iqas hinek kurteroman
j&icirc; hebin, l&ecirc; di esas&ecirc; xwe de roman dir&ecirc;j
e. Di &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; de b&ucirc;yerek an j&icirc; hinek
b&ucirc;yer hene, l&ecirc; di roman&ecirc; de gelek pirr b&ucirc;yer
hene &ucirc; ev hem&ucirc; b&ucirc;yer dikevin nav hev &ucirc;
li hevd&ucirc; t&ecirc;ne honandin&ecirc;. &Ccedil;er&ccedil;eweya
&ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; bi s&icirc;nor e, teng e, l&ecirc; ya
roman&ecirc; fireh e, b&ucirc;yer di gelek cihan de derbas dibe.
Di &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; de &#136;sexs hindik in, di roman&ecirc;
de &#136;sexs pirr in. Di &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; de aliyek&icirc;
&#136;sexsan t&ecirc; dans&icirc;n, di roman&ecirc; de &#136;sexs
bi piral&icirc; t&ecirc;ne danas&icirc;n, taybetiy&ecirc;n w&icirc;
y&ecirc;n pirr al&icirc; t&ecirc; xuyakirin. Li gel van hem&ucirc;
ferqan j&icirc;, di esas&ecirc; xwe de roman &#136;s&ecirc;weyek&icirc;
dir&ecirc;jahiya &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; ye. B&ucirc;yer&ecirc;n
ku di roman&ecirc; de t&ecirc;te qalkirin li ser &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;
ava dibe. Roman, ti&#136;st&ecirc;n ku b&ucirc;ne, yan d&ecirc;
bibe, yan j&icirc; m&ucirc;mk&ucirc;ne ku d&ecirc; bibin qal dike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Taybetiyeke roman &ucirc; &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; ev e ku; bi
meraq t&ecirc; xwendin. Meraqa gir&icirc;ng j&icirc;, gelo d&ecirc;
dawiya w&ecirc; &ccedil;awan bibe ye? Di edebiyat&ecirc; de meraq
c&icirc;hek&icirc; pirr gir&icirc;ng digire. Y&ecirc; ku &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;
dide xwendin meraq e. &Ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;n devk&icirc; j&icirc;
ji ber meraq&ecirc; t&ecirc;t guhdar&icirc;kirin, &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;n
niv&icirc;sk&icirc; j&icirc; ji ber meraq&ecirc; t&ecirc; xwendin.
&Ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;n &#147;Hezar &ucirc; Yek &THORN;ev&quot;
ji ber meraq&ecirc; hatiye guhdar&icirc;kirin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di &ccedil;&icirc;rokniv&icirc;s&ecirc; de karan&icirc;na metoda
meraq&ecirc; her&icirc; ba&#136;s ji al&icirc; niv&icirc;skar&ecirc;
Amer&icirc;k&icirc; Jak London ve hatiye bikaran&icirc;n. Destp&ecirc;ka
&ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;n Jak London li ser meraq&ecirc; hatine
avakirin. Xwendevan ji bo ku di seriya-destp&ecirc;ka- &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;
de meraqa b&ucirc;yer&ecirc; dike -&ucirc; gelo d&ecirc; daw&icirc;
&ccedil;awan be?-, loma j&icirc; hetan&icirc; daw&icirc; w&ecirc;
&ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; dixw&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Wek m&icirc;nak: &Ccedil;&icirc;roka Jak London a bi nav&ecirc;
&#147;Y&ecirc; Meks&icirc;k&icirc;&quot; de di ser&icirc; de meraqeq
gir&icirc;ng heye. Xortek&icirc; 18 sal&icirc;-R&icirc;vera- di&ccedil;e
dikeve nav r&ecirc;xistinek&icirc; &#136;sore&#136;sger. Di w&ecirc;
r&ecirc;xistin&ecirc; de tu kes R&icirc;vera nas nake, kesek bi
derbasb&ucirc;yina jiyana w&icirc; nizane. Wexta ku pere -diraf-
ji r&ecirc;xistin&ecirc; re p&ecirc;w&icirc;st-lazim- dibe, ev
xort-R&icirc;vera- pere t&icirc;ne dide r&ecirc;xistin&ecirc;.
Berpirsiyar&ecirc;n r&ecirc;xistin&ecirc; ji v&ecirc; xort&icirc;
&#136;s&ucirc;phe dikin, dib&ecirc;jin qey ev xort ajan&ecirc;
dewlet&ecirc; ye &ucirc; hatiye ketiye nav wan.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Xwendevan j&icirc; gava v&ecirc; &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; dixw&icirc;ne
di ser&icirc; de meraq dike; gelo derbasb&ucirc;y&icirc;na v&ecirc;
xort&icirc; &ccedil;awan b&ucirc;ye? Ev xort &ccedil;ima ewqas
bi r&ecirc;xistin&ecirc; re al&icirc;kar&icirc; dike? Gelo ev
xort van pereyan ji ko t&icirc;ne? Ev xort bi rast&icirc; j&icirc;
ajan e, yan na?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di b&ucirc;yer&ecirc;n &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; de metod ev e;
xwendevan di seriya b&ucirc;yera &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; de
meraq dike, pa&#136;s&ecirc; j&icirc; ew meraq di nav p&ecirc;vajoya
b&ucirc;yera &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc; de t&ecirc;t pi&#136;skavtin
&ucirc; ew meraqa xwendevan bi rohn&icirc;kirina &ccedil;&icirc;rok&ecirc;
t&ecirc;t f&ecirc;mkirin &ucirc; w&ecirc; gav&ecirc; xwendevan
gava sedema meraq&ecirc; f&ecirc;m dike, dib&ecirc;je ahan...
d&ecirc;meg ev b&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di &ccedil;&icirc;roka &#147;Y&ecirc; Meks&icirc;k&icirc;&quot;
de j&icirc; xwendevan p&ecirc;&#136;s&icirc; meraq dike ku ev
xort&ecirc; al&icirc;gir&ecirc; &#136;sore&#136;sgeran w&ecirc;
perey&icirc; ji ko t&icirc;ne, pa&#136;s&ecirc; f&ecirc;m dibe
ku, ew xort di&ccedil;e ma&ccedil;a boksoriy&ecirc; dike &ucirc;
perey&ecirc; ku ji w&ecirc; qezen&ccedil; dike, t&icirc;ne dide
r&ecirc;xistin&ecirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di edebiyat&ecirc; de rexne, babetek&icirc; gir&icirc;ng e. Ez
bawerim li ser rexnegiriya edeb&icirc; her&icirc; pirr niv&icirc;s
di kovara Helwest&ecirc; de hatiye we&#136;sandin. Edebiyat bi
rexney&ecirc;n edeb&icirc; p&ecirc;&#136;sve di&ccedil;e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di anal&icirc;za berhemek edeb&icirc; de, di h&ucirc;r l&ecirc;n&ecirc;r&icirc;na
berhem&ecirc; de, div&ecirc; mirov ji ko dest p&ecirc; bike? Ji
hunermend&ecirc; berhem&ecirc;, yan ji berhem&ecirc; ve? Yan j&icirc;,
ji &#136;sert &ucirc; &#136;s&ucirc;t&ecirc;n d&icirc;rok&icirc;
&ucirc; civak&icirc; ya w&ecirc; derdor&ecirc; ve?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Div&ecirc; mirov bizanibe, hunermend-niv&icirc;skar- j&icirc;
wek her mirov&icirc;, mirov e-&icirc;nsan e. Ji bo v&ecirc; j&icirc;
mirov berhema edeb&icirc; li gor &#136;sexs &ucirc; qarekter&ecirc;n
niv&icirc;skar&icirc; div&ecirc; nenirx&icirc;ne. Div&ecirc; rexnegir
&ccedil;&ecirc;ker be, xirabker nebe.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Kovara Helwest&ecirc;, d&ecirc; bi berfireh&icirc; c&icirc;h bide
niv&icirc;s&ecirc;n li ser pirs &ucirc; pirsgir&ecirc;k&ecirc;n
edeb&icirc;, niv&icirc;s&ecirc;n rexnegiriya edeb&icirc; &ucirc;
niv&icirc;s&ecirc;n f&ecirc;rb&ucirc;na teoriya edebiyat&ecirc;.
Wek ku me di hejmara s&ecirc;yem de j&icirc; gotib&ucirc;; kovara
Helwest ji bo p&ecirc;&#136;sve&ccedil;&ucirc;na &ccedil;and &ucirc;
edebiyata Kurd&icirc; p&ecirc;ngavek e, div&ecirc; ev p&ecirc;ngav
b&ecirc; xurtkirin.<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&copy; Lokman POLAT
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
</BODY>
