<HTML>
<HEAD>
<META HTTP-EQUIV="Content-Type" CONTENT="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1">
<TITLE>ROMANA KURD</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.03z">
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<HR>
<H2><CENTER><FONT SIZE=6>ROMANA KURD&Icirc; <BR>
</FONT><FONT SIZE=5>Nac&icirc; Kutlay<BR>
</FONT></CENTER></H2>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez pir xemg&icirc;nim k&ucirc; li ser roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc;
nikarim pir ti&#136;stan b&ecirc;jim. Di v&icirc; war&icirc; de
xeberdan wisa ne h&ecirc;sa ye. Ji ber k&ucirc; hejmara roman&ecirc;n
Kurd&icirc; ne z&ecirc;de ne. Em Kurd di war&ecirc; edeb&icirc;yata
niv&icirc;sand&icirc; de pir ne dewlemendin, nemaze di rew&#136;sa
roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; de h&ecirc;j&icirc; pa&#136;s ve mane.
Min dixwest k&ucirc; di prosesa edeb&icirc;yata Kurd&icirc; de
c&icirc;yek&icirc; fireh bidim romanan &ucirc; li ser v&ecirc;
babet&ecirc; bikaribim h&ecirc;j&icirc; z&ecirc;de bipeyivim.
L&ecirc; h&ecirc;v&icirc;darim k&ucirc; ew dem&ecirc;n b&ecirc;n,
roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; y&ecirc; her z&ecirc;de bibin &ucirc;
sal&ecirc;n p&ecirc;&#136;s de Kurd&ecirc;n firset&ecirc;n fireh
bib&icirc;nin &ucirc; minaqe&#136;se bikin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Y&ecirc;n k&ucirc; ez zanim roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; ber&icirc;
1935'a &ccedil;ap neb&ucirc;ne. Li Er&icirc;van&ecirc; romana
Ereb&ecirc; &#136;Semo, &quot;&#136;Sivan&ecirc; Kurd&quot; 1935'an
de hat we&#136;sandin&ecirc;. Pirt&ucirc;k&ecirc;n din, wek Mem
&ucirc; Z&icirc;n, D&icirc;wana Melay&ecirc; Ciz&icirc;r&ecirc;
&ucirc; afrandin&ecirc;n ol&icirc; hatib&ucirc;n &ccedil;apkirin&ecirc;,
l&ecirc; roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; negih&icirc;&#136;stib&ucirc;n
xwendewanan.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ber&icirc; herti&#136;st&icirc;, ez dixwazim di v&icirc; war&icirc;
de &ccedil;end pirsan b&ecirc;jim. Min gelek caran ji xwe &ucirc;
hevalan pirs&icirc;, gelo &ccedil;ima helbest, &ccedil;&icirc;rok
&ucirc; pirt&ucirc;k&ecirc;n d&icirc;n&icirc; hatin niv&icirc;sandin&ecirc;,
l&ecirc; bel&ecirc; roman niv&icirc;sandin awqas&icirc; p&ecirc;&#136;s
de ne&ccedil;&ucirc;?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi d&icirc;tina min &ccedil;end sebeb&ecirc;n gir&icirc;ng hene.
Yek, ew hem&ucirc; dewlet&ecirc;n k&ucirc; Kurd t&ecirc; de dij&icirc;yan,
Kurd&icirc; niv&icirc;sandin ne serbest b&ucirc;. Li Turk&icirc;y&ecirc;
qedehe b&ucirc;, li &Icirc;ran &ucirc; S&ucirc;r&icirc;y&ecirc;
dem dem pir zehmet b&ucirc; &ucirc; li Iraq&ecirc; her h&ecirc;san
b&ucirc;. Di v&ecirc; rew&#136;s&ecirc; de ziman&ecirc; Kurd&icirc;
firset&ecirc;n p&ecirc;&#136;s de &ccedil;&ucirc;yin&ecirc; ned&icirc;t.
Enst&icirc;t&ucirc;, &ccedil;apxane &ucirc; pirt&ucirc;kxan&ecirc;n
taybet&icirc; tuneb&ucirc;n. Lewra j&icirc; ziman&ecirc; Kurd&icirc;,
nemaze di nav Kurd&ecirc;n k&ucirc; li Turk&icirc;y&ecirc; dij&icirc;n,
qels ma. Roman niv&icirc;sandin zimanek&icirc; dewlemend dixwaze.
Meriv xwestin&ecirc;n xwe dikare b&icirc;ne ser ziman, l&ecirc;,
tesw&icirc;r, &icirc;fadekirina bi c&icirc; &ucirc; tem, zimanek&icirc;
her devlemend dixwaze. Wisa nebe, tem &ucirc; lezeta afrandinan
k&ecirc;m dibe. Wek xwerineka b&ecirc; xw&ecirc;, b&ecirc; tem,
p&ecirc; re k&ecirc;fa mer&icirc;ya nay&ecirc;. Kurd&icirc; bi
xwe zimanek&icirc; dewlemend e, l&ecirc; di nav xwend&icirc;yan
de feq&icirc;r maye. Di bajaran de Kurd&icirc; b&ucirc;ye ziman&ecirc;
&ccedil;ar&#136;s&icirc; &ucirc; bazarvan&icirc;y&ecirc;. Ev ziman
t&ecirc;ra p&ecirc;v&icirc;st&icirc;ya j&icirc;yan&ecirc; dike,
l&ecirc; her sal &ucirc; her &ccedil;&ucirc;y&icirc; di h&ecirc;lek&ecirc;
de j&icirc; feq&icirc;r b&ucirc;ye. Bo afrandin&ecirc;n &ccedil;and&icirc;
&ucirc; edeb&icirc;yat&ecirc; ev Kurd&icirc;ya me ya k&ucirc;
li bajar&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc;stan&ecirc; de t&ecirc; xeberdan,
t&ecirc;r&ecirc; nake.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ti&#136;stek&icirc; din j&icirc; heye, roman niv&icirc;sandin
&ucirc; xwendin kar&ecirc; civateka p&ecirc;&#136;s de &ccedil;&ucirc;y&icirc;
ye, xwenday&ecirc;n w&icirc; welat&icirc; gerek&ecirc; z&ecirc;de
bin, ji xwendin&ecirc; hez bikin. Gere em qeb&ucirc;l bikin k&ucirc;,
civata Kurd&icirc; di v&icirc; war&icirc; de gelek&icirc; &#136;s&ucirc;n
ve maye. Jimara xwend&icirc;yan, di van sal&ecirc;n daw&icirc;
de hinek&icirc; z&ecirc;de b&ucirc;n. Hetan&icirc; meriv gelek&icirc;
&ucirc; him j&icirc; gele gelek&icirc; romanan nexw&icirc;ne,
bi xwe nikare roman binv&icirc;se. M&ecirc;j&icirc; gerek bi roman
xwendin&ecirc; t&ecirc;r bibe, tij&icirc; bibe, w&ecirc; &ccedil;ax&ecirc;
demek t&ecirc;, meriv bi xwe j&icirc; dikare ti&#136;st&ecirc;n
n&ucirc; b&icirc;ne hol&ecirc;. Lewra, ez t&ecirc;digih&ecirc;jim
k&ucirc; &ccedil;ima roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; k&ecirc;m in.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez dixwazim b&ecirc;jim k&ucirc;, gelek asteng&ecirc;n me y&ecirc;n
din j&icirc; hene, ez&ecirc; ten&ecirc; wan b&icirc;nim b&icirc;ra
we.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Em Kurd cur be cur elfabeyan kar t&icirc;nin. Taybet&icirc; Kurd&ecirc;n
Turk&icirc;yay&ecirc; herf&ecirc;n elfaba Ereb&icirc; nizanin,
ji ber v&ecirc; yek&ecirc;, ew roman&ecirc;n k&ucirc; Kurd&ecirc;n
&Icirc;ran&ecirc;, S&ucirc;r&icirc;y&ecirc; anj&icirc; Iraq&ecirc;
niv&icirc;s&icirc;ne, em nikarin wan bixw&icirc;nin. Bi v&icirc;
tehr&icirc; y&ecirc;n Sovyet&icirc;stan a ber&ecirc; ji bi t&icirc;p&ecirc;n
Kr&icirc;l&icirc; ne. Her &ccedil;iqas&icirc; j&icirc; Kurd&ecirc;n
&Icirc;ran, Iraq, R&ucirc;syay&ecirc; &ucirc; S&ucirc;riy&ecirc;
t&icirc;p&ecirc;n lat&icirc;n&icirc; bizanibin, d&icirc;saj&icirc;
zehmet&icirc;y&ecirc; diki&#136;s&icirc;nin, bi t&icirc;p&ecirc;n
lat&icirc;n&icirc; re pir k&ecirc;fxwe&#136;s n&icirc;nin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
X&ecirc;nj&icirc; van zehmet&icirc;yan, em dizanin k&ucirc;, niha
Kurd li hem&ucirc; welat&ecirc;n Avr&ucirc;pay&ecirc; bela b&ucirc;ne,
li wan deran bi hal&ecirc; penaber&icirc;y&ecirc; de dij&icirc;n.
Hinek ji van Kurdan roman anj&icirc; pirt&ucirc;k&ecirc;n din
diniv&icirc;sin. L&ecirc; bel&ecirc; pirt&ucirc;k belav kirin
di nav Kurd&ecirc;n Avr&ucirc;pay&ecirc; de nehatine organ&icirc;ze
kirin. Lewra j&icirc;, romaneka Kurd&icirc; li van welatan k&ucirc;
&ccedil;ap dibe, dereng anj&icirc; qet nagih&ecirc;je dest&ecirc;
Kurd&ecirc;n k&ucirc; welat&ecirc;n din de dij&icirc;n. Caran
haya mer&icirc;ya j&icirc; qet p&ecirc; nabe. Ev hal bi ser&ecirc;
xwe astengeka mezin e.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di nav van asteng&icirc;yan, yek j&icirc; eve k&ucirc;, di Kurd&icirc;
de zarav&ecirc;n me y&ecirc;n cur bi cur, ji hev d&ucirc;r in.
Y&ecirc;k k&ucirc; Soran&icirc;, Kurmanc&icirc; anj&icirc; Zazak&icirc;
binv&icirc;sin, gelek&icirc; ji hev fem nakin. Zarav&ecirc;n romanan
gir&icirc;ng e, dema k&ucirc; meriv w&icirc; zarav&icirc; ba&#136;s
nizanibe, meriv tem &ucirc; xwe&#136;s&icirc;ya roman&ecirc; hilnade.
K&ecirc;fa mer&icirc;ya p&ecirc; re nay&ecirc;. Bo xwendin &ucirc;
niv&icirc;sandin&ecirc; gere meriv w&icirc; zarav&icirc; ba&#136;s
bizanibe.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Kovar&ecirc;n li ser edeb&#155;yat &ucirc; &ccedil;anda Kurd&icirc;,
y&ecirc;n merkez&icirc; k&ecirc;m in. Ev k&ecirc;mas&icirc;yeke
mezin e. Y&ecirc;n hey&icirc; j&icirc; bi herem&icirc;n e, nagih&ecirc;jin
dest&ecirc;n pir xwendewanan. Lewra j&icirc; gelek xwendewan ji
roman&ecirc;n &ccedil;apb&ucirc;y&icirc; b&ecirc;xeber dim&icirc;nin.
Di v&icirc; war&icirc; de &icirc;nst&icirc;tu &ucirc; r&ecirc;xistin&ecirc;n
kultur&icirc; k&ecirc;m in &ucirc; hewcedar&icirc;y&ecirc; nikarin
b&icirc;nin c&icirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ziman&ecirc; Kurd&icirc; bi r&icirc;tm &ucirc; deng&ecirc; xwe
ve, ji bo helbestan gelek&icirc; ba&#136;s e. Yek&ecirc; j&icirc;,
trad&icirc;syona helbest niv&icirc;sandin&ecirc; di nav Kurdan
de pir kevn e. Bi &ccedil;end sed salan vir de helbest&ecirc;n
devk&icirc; hatine gotin&ecirc; &ucirc; n&ecirc;z&icirc;k&icirc;
7-8 sed salin k&ucirc; helbest&ecirc;n niv&icirc;s&icirc; di edeb&icirc;ta
Kurd&icirc; de c&icirc;h girt&icirc;ye. Ji bo w&ecirc; j&icirc;,
helbest niv&icirc;sandin her h&ecirc;sa ye, em Kurd him ji bo
aheng, r&icirc;tm &ucirc; deng&ecirc;n w&ecirc; y&icirc; k&ucirc;
hez &ucirc; k&ecirc;f&ecirc; dide &icirc;nsanan, gelek helbest
hatine niv&icirc;sandin. K&ecirc;m kesan ber&ecirc; xwe dane niv&icirc;sandina
romanan.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; bel&ecirc;, gere em tu car&icirc; b&icirc;rnekin k&ucirc;
ji bo van k&ecirc;mas&icirc; &ucirc; astengan yek &ccedil;are
heye, ew j&icirc; her z&ecirc;de Kurd&icirc; bixw&icirc;nin &ucirc;
binv&icirc;sin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Van zehmet&icirc; &ucirc; astenga, yek ji niv&icirc;skar&ecirc;n
Kurd&ecirc;n Sovyet&icirc;stan a ber&ecirc;, &Ccedil;erkez&ecirc;
Re&#136;s di p&ecirc;&#136;sgotina romana El&icirc;y&ecirc; Evdirrehman
&quot;&#136;Ser &Ccedil;&icirc;yada&quot; bi v&icirc; tehr&icirc;
t&icirc;ne ser ziman: &quot;...Pirs ewe, wek&icirc; roman janra
l&icirc;teratur&icirc;y&ecirc; ye here giran, &ccedil;etin &ucirc;
sexte.&quot;
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Hine niv&icirc;skar bi esl&ecirc; xwe ve Kurd in, l&ecirc;, afrandin&ecirc;
xwe bi taybet&icirc; Tirk&icirc;, Faris&icirc;, Ereb&icirc;, R&ucirc;s&icirc;
anj&icirc; bi zimanek&icirc; din niv&icirc;s&icirc;ne. Naverok&ecirc;n
van berheman di derheq&ecirc; Kurdan bin j&icirc;, wek edeta din&ecirc;,
ev kesan &ucirc; ev pirt&ucirc;k &ucirc; romanan &quot;berhem&ecirc;n
Kurd&icirc;&quot; nay&ecirc;n qeb&ucirc;l kirin. Niv&icirc;skar&ecirc;n
wisa, y&ecirc;n bi gelek giranbiha di wan hem&ucirc; welat&ecirc;n
k&ucirc; Kurd t&ecirc; de dij&icirc;n hene. Ne hewceye em yek
yek nav&ecirc;n van hunermendan b&ecirc;jin. L&ecirc; ev heval&ecirc;n
b&ecirc;hempa, bi qedr &ucirc; q&icirc;met in, bi k&icirc;jan
ziman&icirc; niv&icirc;s&icirc;ne bi w&icirc; tehr&icirc; &quot;niv&icirc;skar&quot;
t&ecirc;n qeb&ucirc;l kirin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di j&icirc;yana hem&ucirc; gelan de demek hat&icirc;ye, pirs&ecirc;n
civak&icirc;, y&ecirc;n gund&icirc;t&icirc;y&ecirc; li p&ecirc;&#136;s
hem&ucirc; pirsan ket&icirc;ye. Ji ber v&icirc; sebeb&icirc;,
ev babet, gund&icirc;t&icirc; di romanan de c&icirc;h girt&icirc;ye.
L&ecirc; j&icirc;yan k&ucirc; hat&icirc;ye guhartin &ucirc; ber
bi b&ucirc;rj&ucirc;waz&icirc;y&ecirc; -bazarvan&icirc;y&ecirc;-
&ccedil;&ucirc;ye, v&ecirc; guhartin&ecirc; xwe di hem&ucirc;
cur&ecirc;n edeb&icirc;yat&ecirc; de n&icirc;&#136;san daye, her
wisa, di romanan de j&icirc;. Ev naverok guhartin ne bi xwestina
me dibe, ji ber zorday&icirc;na j&icirc;yan&ecirc; ev b&ucirc;yer
p&ecirc;k t&ecirc;n. Bi ya min, ev ti&#136;st y&ecirc; di edeb&icirc;yata
Kurd&icirc; de j&icirc; wisa bibe. Ana durif&ecirc; &quot;gund&icirc;t&icirc;&quot;y&ecirc;
li ser edeb&icirc;yata Kurd&icirc; ye. Meriv ku li roman, &ccedil;&icirc;rok
&ucirc; helbest&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; dinh&ecirc;re, v&ecirc; rast&icirc;y&ecirc;
dib&icirc;ne. Hela edeb&icirc;yat&ecirc; bidin al&icirc;k&icirc;,
babeta gund&icirc;t&icirc;y&ecirc; xwe pir al&icirc; ve n&icirc;&#136;san
dide. H&ucirc;n nav&ecirc;n me y&ecirc;n &quot;anon&icirc;m&quot;
binih&ecirc;rin, &quot;Gund&icirc;, Gavan, &#136;Sivan, &Ccedil;&icirc;ya,
Berxvan...&quot; nav&ecirc;n her&icirc; z&ecirc;de ne. Ev ti&#136;stek&icirc;
pir normal e k&ucirc; edeb&icirc;yata me j&icirc; demeka d&ucirc;r-dir&ecirc;j
w&ecirc; &quot;gund&icirc;&quot; be.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Civat k&ucirc; p&ecirc;&#136;s de di&ccedil;e, meriv h&ecirc;d&icirc;
h&ecirc;d&icirc; ferq dike k&ucirc; l&icirc;teratura w&ecirc;
civat&ecirc; j&icirc;, ne bi lez be j&icirc;, p&ecirc;&#136;s
de di&ccedil;e &ucirc; t&ecirc; guhartin&ecirc;. &Icirc;&#136;saret&ecirc;n
guhartin&ecirc; di nav edeb&icirc;yata Kurd&icirc; de xwe dide
xuyakirin. Guhartina edeb&icirc;yat&ecirc; di pey guhartina civat&ecirc;
xwe n&icirc;&#136;san dide.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; bi p&icirc;van&ecirc;n navnetew&icirc; ve, ez roman&ecirc;n
Kurd&icirc; qels dib&icirc;nim. Rohat, ji bo Kurd&ecirc;n k&ucirc;
k&ecirc;mas&icirc; 20 m&icirc;lyon in &ucirc; meriv ten&ecirc;
dikare nav&ecirc;n qas&icirc; 20 romana b&icirc;ne ser ziman,
w&ecirc;ya k&ecirc;mas&icirc;ke mezin dib&icirc;ne. L&ecirc; d&icirc;saj&icirc;
di kovara &quot;N&ucirc;dem&quot;&ecirc; de p&ecirc;&#136;seroj&ecirc;n
gelek&icirc; tar&icirc; n&icirc;&#136;san nade.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Niv&icirc;skar&ecirc; romana &quot;Labirenta Cinan&quot; Hesen&ecirc;
Met&ecirc; di hempey&icirc;v&icirc;na xwe ya di N&ucirc;dem'&ecirc;
de, di v&icirc; war&icirc; de awha dib&ecirc;je: &quot;...K&ecirc;m
z&ecirc;de romana Kurd&icirc; j&icirc; di rew&#136;sa &ccedil;&icirc;roka
Kurd&icirc; de ye...&quot; &quot;...Em vegerin ser roman&ecirc;n
xwe. Min berhem&ecirc;n h&ecirc;ja bi Kurd&icirc; j&icirc; xwendine.
Lezeta roman &ucirc; novel&ecirc;n k&ucirc; min ji p&ecirc;n&ucirc;s&ecirc;n
biyan&icirc; girt&icirc;ye, di berhem&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; de j&icirc;
ez rast&icirc; wan lezetan hatime. L&ecirc; mixabin, heb&ucirc;na
niv&icirc;skarek&icirc; &ucirc; romaneke bi v&ecirc; lezet&ecirc;
ji bo min t&ecirc;r nake k&ucirc; ez behsa romana Kurd&icirc;
bikim &ucirc; bidim ber roman&ecirc;n navnetew&icirc;...&quot;
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Yek&icirc; k&ucirc; di nav Kurdan de pirtir roman niv&icirc;s&icirc;ye,
Memet Uzun e. Ew di v&icirc; war&icirc; de roj&ecirc;n p&ecirc;&#136;s
ronah&icirc; dib&icirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez dikarim bi kurt&icirc; hinek&icirc; j&icirc; qala van roman&ecirc;n
k&ucirc; min bi destxistine &ucirc; xwendine, anj&icirc; y&ecirc;n
k&ucirc; derheq&ecirc; wan de zanadar&icirc;ya min heye, bikim.
<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
ROMAN&Ecirc;N KURD&Ecirc;N SOVYET&Icirc;STANA BER&Ecirc;
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Ez dikarim bi taybet&icirc; &ccedil;end x&ucirc;s&ucirc;s&icirc;yet&ecirc;n
wan niv&icirc;skar &ucirc; roman&ecirc;n wan b&ecirc;jim. Gelek&ecirc;n
wan Kurd&ecirc;n Osman&icirc; b&ucirc;n &ucirc; pi&#136;st&icirc;
&#136;Ser&ecirc; Dinyay&ecirc; y&icirc; Yekem&icirc;n ji Kurd&icirc;stana
Tirk&icirc;yay&ecirc;, derdora Qers'&ecirc;, Wan'&ecirc; &ucirc;
w&icirc;layet&ecirc;n din rev&icirc;b&ucirc;n, &ccedil;&ucirc;b&ucirc;n
Ermen&icirc;stan &ucirc; Gurc&icirc;stan&ecirc;. Hema gi&#136;st
j&icirc; Kurd&ecirc;n Ezd&icirc; ne. Serp&ecirc;hat&icirc;y&ecirc;n
xwe de dib&ecirc;jin k&ucirc;, &quot;em ji ber zora Rom&ecirc;
rev&icirc;yan.&quot; Naveroka berhem&ecirc;n wan gelek cara li
ser w&ecirc; dem&ecirc; ye. Pi&#136;st&icirc; wan roj&ecirc;n
bi bir&ccedil;&icirc;b&ucirc;n, rev &ucirc; qirb&ucirc;n&ecirc;,
di bin rej&icirc;ma sosyal&icirc;zm&ecirc; digih&ecirc;jine j&icirc;yaneka
b&ecirc;tirs &ucirc; ba&#136;s. Dibistan&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; de
dixw&icirc;nin &ucirc; radyoy&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; guhdar&icirc;
dikin. Piran&icirc;ya roman&ecirc;n wan di v&ecirc; naverok&ecirc;
de nin. Wek niv&icirc;skar&ecirc;n din li Sovyet&icirc;stan&ecirc;,
ew j&icirc; sosyal&icirc;zm&ecirc; meth &ucirc; sena dikin. Bi
ya min di v&icirc; war&icirc; de hinek&icirc; j&icirc; p&ecirc;&#136;s
de di&ccedil;in &ucirc; w&ecirc; &ccedil;ax&ecirc; lezeta van
romanan k&ecirc;m dibe.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; ev e&#136;skere ye k&ucirc;, roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc;
ber&ecirc; p&ecirc;&#136;s&icirc;n bi dest&ecirc;n Kurd&ecirc;n
Sovyet&ecirc; t&ecirc;n&ecirc; niv&icirc;sandin. Y&ecirc; her&icirc;
ewil j&icirc; Ereb &#136;Sam&icirc;lov e. Ji bo w&icirc; gelek
kes &quot;Bav&ecirc; roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc;&quot; dib&ecirc;jin.
<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
R o m a n &ecirc; n E r e b &#136;S a m &icirc; l o v:
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di roman&ecirc;n xwe de xezan&icirc;, feq&icirc;r&icirc; &ucirc;
j&icirc;yana Kurd&ecirc;n w&ecirc; dem&ecirc; -sal&ecirc;n pi&#136;st&icirc;
&#136;Ser&ecirc; Dinya y&icirc; Yekem&icirc;n- t&icirc;ne p&ecirc;&#136;s
me. Bindest&icirc;, feq&icirc;r&icirc;, roj&ecirc;n re&#136;s
&ucirc; d&icirc;sa di w&ecirc; dem&ecirc; de dil&#136;sah&icirc;,
azad&icirc; &ucirc; h&ecirc;v&icirc;kirin&ecirc; wek s&ecirc;veka
tir&#136;s bi me dide xwarin&ecirc;. Romana w&icirc; ya ewl&icirc;n,
&quot;&#136;Sivan&ecirc; Kurd&quot; e. Serp&ecirc;hat&icirc;ya
niv&icirc;skar bi xwe &ucirc; rew&#136;sa Kurdan di roman&ecirc;
de bi hev re di&ccedil;e. Roman li Er&icirc;van'&ecirc; sala 1935'an
de &ccedil;ap b&ucirc;. 1978'an de li Estenbol'e hat we&#136;sandin.
Pa&#136;s&ecirc; &#136;Sivan&ecirc; Kurd bi nav&ecirc; &quot;Berbang&quot;
d&icirc;sa li Er&icirc;van'&ecirc;, 1959'an de &ccedil;ap b&ucirc;.
Roman serp&ecirc;hat&icirc;ya Ereb &#136;Semo ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Romana &quot;J&icirc;yana Bextewar&quot; &ucirc; &quot;Hopo&quot;
li Er&icirc;van'&ecirc; 1969'an de di &quot;Beravok&quot;&ecirc;
de &ccedil;ap dibin. Kurd&ecirc;n ko&ccedil;er ji Turk&icirc;y&ecirc;
&ccedil;awa direvin t&ecirc;n Sovyet&icirc;stan&ecirc; &ucirc;
pa&#136;s&ecirc; roj&ecirc;n qenc dil&#136;say&icirc;y&ecirc;
dib&icirc;nin, naveroka van romanan e. Ereb &#136;Semo behsa j&icirc;yaneka
n&ucirc;, p&ecirc;&#136;s de &ccedil;&ucirc;yin &ucirc; avakirina
sosyal&icirc;zm&ecirc; dike. Romana w&icirc; ya &ccedil;ara &quot;Dimdim&quot;
1966'an de d&icirc;sa li Er&icirc;van'&ecirc; &ccedil;ap dibe.
Romaneka d&icirc;rok&icirc; ye. Li Kurd&icirc;stana &Icirc;ran&ecirc;,
Xan&ecirc; Kurd Lepz&ecirc;r&icirc;n -&Ccedil;epz&ecirc;r&icirc;n-
bi &ccedil;end e&#136;s&icirc;r&ecirc;n din ve dij&icirc; &#136;Sah&ecirc;
&Icirc;ran&ecirc; Ebbas&ecirc; Duyem re &#136;ser dike. Kurd di
kela Dimdim&ecirc; de, &Icirc;ran&icirc; ava wan dibirin, l&ecirc;
jin, b&ucirc;k &ucirc; m&ecirc;r heta mirin&ecirc; ber xwe didin.
Romana Dimdim li Sw&ecirc;d&ecirc; sala 1983'an de d&icirc;sa
&ccedil;ap b&ucirc;. <BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
E l &icirc; y &ecirc; E v d i r r e h m a n
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Romana &quot;Xat&ecirc; Xanim&quot; 1958'an de hate we&#136;sandin.
Li ser kurd&ecirc;n Tirk&icirc;yay&ecirc; hat&icirc;ye niv&icirc;sandin.
Xat&ecirc; Xanim Dersim&icirc; ye, m&ecirc;r&ecirc; w&ecirc; k&ucirc;
dimre, wek m&ecirc;ran e&#136;s&icirc;ra xwe r&ecirc;va dibe &ucirc;
dij&icirc; dewlet&ecirc; &#136;ser dike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Romana &quot;Gund&ecirc; M&ecirc;rxasa&quot;, d&icirc;sa rew&#136;sa
Kurd&ecirc;n k&ucirc; li Tirk&icirc;yay&ecirc; pi&#136;st&icirc;
&#136;Ser&ecirc; &#136;S&ecirc;x Se&icirc;d penaber b&ucirc;n
hatin Sovyet&icirc;stan&ecirc;, p&ecirc;&#136;sber&icirc; xwendewanan
dike. 5700 mal mihacir dibin. Di Sovyet&icirc;stan&ecirc; derg&ecirc;
x&ecirc;r&ecirc;, xwe&#136;s&icirc;y&ecirc;, xwendin &ucirc; p&ecirc;&#136;s
de &ccedil;&ucirc;yin&ecirc; dib&icirc;nin. L&ecirc; bi ya min
di v&ecirc; roman&ecirc; de El&icirc;y&ecirc; Evdirrehman xwe
dike zehmet&icirc;ke giran, dema k&ucirc; Xezal a ke&ccedil;a
serok&ecirc; e&#136;s&icirc;r&ecirc; dike kom&icirc;n&icirc;st&ecirc;
ciwan -komsomol-, bi dest&ecirc; wan r&ecirc;xistin&ecirc;n sosyal&icirc;st&icirc;
p&ecirc;&#136;sber&icirc; xwendewanan dike. Ev roman j&icirc;
li Er&icirc;van'&ecirc;, 1968'an de &ccedil;ap b&ucirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Romana &quot;&#136;Ser &Ccedil;&icirc;yada&quot;, 1989'an de li
Er&icirc;van&ecirc; hat we&#136;sandin. El&icirc;y&ecirc; Evdirrehman
ji bo naveroka v&ecirc; roman&ecirc; bi xwe dib&ecirc;je k&ucirc;:
&quot;... Eva nemaze li ser &#136;ser&ecirc; Kurdan, di nav sal&ecirc;n
1928-1930'an li bereka Gir&icirc;dax&ecirc; ye, wek&icirc; Kurdan
nava wan salan da li p&ecirc;&#136;sa Gir&icirc;dax&ecirc; &#136;serek&icirc;
&ccedil;away&icirc; giran dan&icirc;ne...&quot; Meriv ji niv&icirc;skar
&ucirc; p&ecirc;&#136;sgotin&ecirc; fem dike k&ucirc; gere ev
roman du pirt&ucirc;k bin. Di ya duem&icirc;n de li ser r&ecirc;vabir&ecirc;n
&#136;Ser&ecirc; Gir&icirc;dax&ecirc; &Icirc;hsan N&ucirc;r&icirc;
&ucirc; Biroy&ecirc; Hesik&ecirc; Tell&icirc; bihata niv&icirc;sandin&ecirc;.
L&ecirc; mixabin ev pirt&ucirc;k derneket &ucirc; niv&icirc;skar
&ccedil;&ucirc; ber rehma Xwed&ecirc;. Qehreman&ecirc; y&icirc;
sereke di romana &#136;Ser &Ccedil;&icirc;yada &#136;S&ecirc;x
Zahir e. Min bi xwe j&icirc; derheq&ecirc; &#136;S&ecirc;x Zahir
de gelek ti&#136;st bih&icirc;stin. Meta min Bes&ecirc; di nav
&#136;Ser&ecirc; Gir&icirc;dax&ecirc; de b&ucirc;, her tim qala
&#136;S&ecirc;x Zahir &ucirc; Simbil'&ecirc; dikir. Simbil q&icirc;za
Mehm&ucirc;d Beg&ecirc; Torina Mala Kose b&ucirc;. &#136;S&ecirc;x
Zahir Simbil bi zor&ecirc; revandib&ucirc;. Simbil'&ecirc; ev
yek qeb&ucirc;l nekir &ucirc; xwe bi tivinga &#136;S&ecirc;x Zahir
ku&#136;st. W&ecirc; dem&ecirc; meta min j&icirc; li wir b&ucirc;.
Ev b&ucirc;yer di roman&ecirc; de tunin. Roman &#136;S&ecirc;x
Zahir bi tehrek&icirc; din n&icirc;&#136;san dide. Bi ya min ev
&#136;sa&#136;s e, xelet&icirc; ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di roman&ecirc;n d&icirc;rok&icirc; de meriv &quot;&#136;sexsan&quot;
&ucirc; &quot;qehreman&ecirc;n roman&ecirc;&quot; nikare bi tehrek&icirc;
din n&icirc;&#136;san bide. Taybet&icirc; qehreman k&ucirc; di
nav xelq&ecirc; de yek&icirc; nas be, meriv nikare &#136;sexs&icirc;yet&ecirc;
w&icirc; biguhur&icirc;ne. &#136;S&ecirc;x Zahir nexwend&icirc;b&ucirc;,
li h&ecirc;la Qers&ecirc; &ucirc; Gir&icirc;dax&ecirc; b&ucirc;.
Di roman&ecirc; de yek&icirc; xwend&icirc; ye &ucirc; hezkir&icirc;ya
xwe, li Wan'&ecirc; ji dibistan&ecirc; hildide, t&ecirc;n Gir&icirc;dax&ecirc;
&ucirc; bi tev &#136;ser dikin. Ya din, El&icirc;y&ecirc; Evdirrehman
di roman&ecirc; de Kurdan gelek&icirc; qehreman n&icirc;&#136;san
dide &ucirc; Tirkan bi zaneb&ucirc;n neba&#136;s p&ecirc;&#136;sber
dike, l&ecirc; daw&icirc; y&ecirc; de nikare bo serneketina Kurdan
re sebeb&ecirc;n taybet&icirc; bib&icirc;ne... H&ecirc;lek bi
s&icirc;lah &ucirc; jimar z&ecirc;de ne, bi top &ucirc; balafir
in. L&ecirc; di roman&ecirc; de Kurd wisa qehreman in k&ucirc;
meriv t&ecirc;nagih&ecirc;je k&ucirc; &ccedil;ima Kurd bindikevin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Niv&icirc;skar&ecirc; ez&icirc;z El&icirc;y&ecirc; Evdirrehman
di 1984'an de di hempeyiv&icirc;neka xwe de e&#136;skere kir k&ucirc;
li ser romanek&ecirc; k&ucirc; bi nav&ecirc; &quot;Murtule Beg&quot;
dixebite. L&ecirc; mixabin k&ucirc; em nizanin ev xebata &ccedil;i
b&ucirc;. Ji bo Murtule Beg'&ecirc; niv&icirc;skar, &quot;&ccedil;awa
t&ecirc; zan&icirc;n ew xwe&#136;sm&ecirc;r&ecirc; nav&ccedil;a
M&ucirc;ks&ecirc; b&ucirc;...&quot; dib&ecirc;je.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
