roman&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc; li Turk&icirc;y&ecirc; pirr gereng destp&ecirc;kir&icirc;ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Eger &#136;sa&#136;s n&icirc;n bim, ya her&icirc; ewl&icirc;n,
romana Memet &Ucirc;z&ucirc;n bi nav&ecirc; &quot;Tu&quot; ye.
Memet xwast&icirc;ye roman&ecirc; bi curek&icirc; modern binv&icirc;se.
Lewra, ne bi tehr&ecirc; klas&icirc;k e romana Tu. Rew&#136;sa
xelq&ecirc; me Kurda k&ucirc; li gund&ecirc;n derdora S&icirc;wereg&ecirc;
dij&icirc;n, t&ecirc;n ser ziman. N&ucirc;b&ucirc;n, d&icirc;tin&ecirc;n
ciwanan &ucirc; y&ecirc;n bi sal z&ecirc;de dide ber hev. Caran
d&icirc;tin&ecirc;n felsef&icirc; dike tev. Roman&ecirc; bala
gelek kes&icirc; ki&#136;sand, l&ecirc; ne bi tehr&ecirc; roman&ecirc;n
k&ucirc; heta niha Kurdan xwendib&ucirc;n, lewra bi gelek kesan
re j&icirc; &quot;ec&ecirc;b&quot; hat, lezet &ucirc; tem j&ecirc;
negirtin. &Icirc;&#136;skence &ucirc; ruh&icirc;yeta girt&icirc;k&icirc;
t&ecirc; anal&icirc;z kirin. Roman 1984'an de li Stockholm&ecirc;
&ccedil;ap b&ucirc;. 
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; Memet &Ucirc;z&ucirc;n xebat&ecirc;n xwe y&ecirc;n li
ser roman niv&icirc;sandin&ecirc; her p&ecirc;&#136;s de bir.
Naverok&ecirc;n roman&ecirc;n xwe ji kes&ecirc;n d&icirc;rok&icirc;
y&ecirc;n Kurdan digirt. Wek li ser j&icirc;yana Dengb&ecirc;j&ecirc;
bi nav &ucirc; deng Evdal&ecirc; Zeynik&ecirc;, Sekreter&ecirc;
Xoyb&ucirc;n&ecirc; Memd&ucirc;h Sel&icirc;m &ucirc; h&icirc;mdar&ecirc;
elifbaya Kurd&icirc; ya lat&icirc;n&icirc;, zimanzan&ecirc; mezin
Celadet Bedirxan roman niv&icirc;s&icirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
1987'an de romana Memet &Ucirc;z&ucirc;n ya duem&icirc;n d&icirc;sa
li Stockholm&ecirc; &ccedil;ap b&ucirc;. Nav&ecirc; w&ecirc;,
&quot;Mirina Kalek&icirc; Rind&quot; b&ucirc;. Di v&ecirc; roman&ecirc;
de kult&ucirc;ra Kurdan, ya nesla kevn &ucirc; n&ucirc; t&icirc;ne
p&ecirc;&#136;s hev. Ev herd &ccedil;&icirc;n bi hev re &#136;serek&icirc;
b&ecirc;deng dikin... Memet &Ucirc;z&ucirc;n, trad&icirc;syona
kevn &ucirc; n&ucirc; n&icirc;&#136;san&icirc; me dide. Trad&icirc;syona
n&ucirc; bi &ccedil;i tehr&icirc; dixwaze li ser bikeve? Xetatek&icirc;
kal, qehremanek&icirc; roman&ecirc; ye. &quot;Kalo&quot; &ucirc;
qehreman&ecirc; din y&ecirc; ciwan j&icirc; Serdar Axad e. Kalo
y&ecirc; xetat afrandin&ecirc; Melay&ecirc; Ciz&icirc;r&ecirc;
bi dest&ecirc;n xwe y&ecirc;n hunermend neqi&#136;sand&icirc;ye.
Daw&icirc;y&ecirc; de hat&icirc;ye li gundek&icirc; de c&icirc;
b&ucirc;ye. Wek yek&icirc; penaber e. Bil&ucirc;r&ecirc;, teb&icirc;et&ecirc;,
rind&icirc;y&ecirc; &ucirc; ba&#136;s&icirc;y&ecirc; hez dike.
Di roman&ecirc; de hal&ecirc; penaber&icirc;y&ecirc;, mihacir&icirc;y&ecirc;
t&ecirc; anal&icirc;z kirin. Meriv hal&ecirc;n wan&ecirc;n h&icirc;ss&icirc;
&ucirc; ruh&icirc; dixw&icirc;ne. 
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di van herd roman&ecirc;n Memet &Ucirc;z&ucirc;n de taybet&icirc;
hinek kes &ucirc; b&ucirc;yer ne zelal in. L&ecirc; di romana
xwe ya s&ecirc;em&icirc;n de ji &quot;anon&icirc;m&icirc;&quot;y&ecirc;
derdikeve, her ti&#136;st&icirc; e&#136;skere &ucirc; zelal dide
p&ecirc;&#136;s me. Romana s&ecirc;em&icirc;n, &quot;S&icirc;ya
Ev&icirc;n&ecirc;&quot; ye. Qehreman&ecirc; roman&ecirc; Memd&ucirc;h
Sel&icirc;m e. Memd&ucirc;h Sel&icirc;m ji h&ecirc;la Wan&ecirc;
ye. Li Estenbol&ecirc; ronakb&icirc;r &ucirc; welatpar&ecirc;zek&icirc;
Kurd e. Pa&#136;s&ecirc;, dema k&ucirc; C&ucirc;mh&ucirc;r&icirc;yeta
T&icirc;rk&icirc;y&ecirc; ava dibe, di&ccedil;e li S&ucirc;r&icirc;y&ecirc;
c&icirc; dibe. Kesek&icirc; modern e. Yek ji h&icirc;mdar&ecirc;
Xoyb&ucirc;n'&ecirc; ye. Li wir ke&ccedil;eka &Ccedil;erkez hez
dike, l&ecirc; w&ecirc; dem&ecirc; ber&ecirc; xwe dide Ararat'&ecirc;
-Gir&icirc;dax&ecirc;-, tev&icirc; &#136;Sore&#136;sa Ararat&ecirc;
dibe. Pi&#136;st&icirc; belavb&ucirc;na &#136;Sore&#136;sa Ararat&ecirc;
vedigere. L&ecirc; dib&icirc;ne k&ucirc; ke&ccedil;a &Ccedil;erkez
bi yek&icirc; din re zewic&icirc;ye. Di roman&ecirc; de rew&#136;sa
ciwata Kurd, r&ecirc;vabirina &#136;Sore&#136;sa Ararat&ecirc;
&ucirc; ev&icirc;na ke&ccedil;a &Ccedil;erkez xwe&#136;s hat&icirc;ye
p&ecirc;&#136;s xwendewanan.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Romana Memet &Ucirc;z&ucirc;n ya &ccedil;arem&icirc;n, &quot;Rojek
Ji Roj&ecirc;n Evdal&ecirc; Zeynik&ecirc;&quot; ye. Evdal&ecirc;
Zeynik&ecirc; dengb&ecirc;jek&icirc; gelek&icirc; bi nav &ucirc;
deng e. Ji derdora Ararat&ecirc;, Ela&#136;sgir, Qereyaz&icirc;,
Milazgir &ucirc; Dutax'&ecirc; ye. Bi tehrek&icirc; din k&ucirc;
ez b&ecirc;jim, Evdal&ecirc; Zeynik&ecirc; hembajar&icirc;y&ecirc;
-hem&#136;sehr&icirc;- min t&ecirc; hesab kirin&ecirc;. Em serhed&icirc;,
derheq&ecirc; w&icirc; de gelek ti&#136;stan zanin. Bi kurtay&icirc;
dikarim b&ecirc;jim, ew qurna 19'an de j&icirc;yaye. Dengb&ecirc;j&ecirc;
Surmel&icirc; Memed Paa&#136;sa b&ucirc;. Surmel&icirc; Memed
Pa&#136;sa li Ela&#136;sgir'&ecirc; -Toraqqel&ecirc;- r&ucirc;dini&#136;st.
Beg&ecirc; Serhed'&ecirc; y&icirc; mezin b&ucirc;. Bi esker&ecirc;n
xwe ve &ccedil;&ucirc; al&icirc;kar&icirc;ya Siltan&ecirc; Osman&icirc;
kir li Kozan'&ecirc;, &#136;ser&ecirc; Kozanoxl&icirc; kir. Li
ber germa Eden&ecirc; pirr kes&ecirc;n w&icirc; qir b&ucirc;n.
Kilama &quot;Li Xozan&ecirc;...Li Xozan&ecirc;&quot; li ser v&ecirc;
b&ucirc;yer&ecirc; ye. Dengb&ecirc;jek&icirc; navdar, nav&ecirc;
w&icirc; Sil&ecirc;, xelq&ecirc; D&icirc;yarbekr&ecirc; re bi
kilaman ve ber hev didin, dikevin lec&ecirc;. Ava re&#136;s t&ecirc;
li ser &ccedil;ev&ecirc;n Evdal&ecirc; Zeynik&ecirc;. Demeke d&ucirc;r-dir&ecirc;j
Evdal&ecirc; Zeynik&ecirc; &ecirc;d&icirc; nab&icirc;ne. Nav&ecirc;
kur&ecirc; w&icirc; Temo &ucirc; jina w&icirc; Gul&ecirc; ye.
Qulingek&icirc; topal &ucirc; bask &#136;sikest&icirc; xwe re
dike heval &ucirc; quling pak dike. Kilam&ecirc;n xwe li ser &quot;Quling,
Temo, Gul&ecirc; &ucirc; teb&icirc;et&ecirc;&quot; got&icirc;ye.
Di roman&ecirc;n Ya&#136;sar Kemal de, pirr caran qala Evdal&ecirc;
Zeynik&ecirc; t&ecirc; kirin&ecirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; di romana Memet &Ucirc;z&ucirc;n de qala b&ucirc;yer&ecirc;n
Surmel&icirc; Memed Pa&#136;sa &ucirc; &#136;ser&ecirc; Kozan'&ecirc;
nay&ecirc; kirin. 1935'an de y&ecirc;n k&ucirc; kovara Hewar'&ecirc;
derdixin, du bira Celadet &ucirc; Kam&ucirc;ran Bedirxan Beg dixwazin
k&ucirc; heval&ecirc;n wa y&icirc; dengb&ecirc;j Ehmed&ecirc;
Ferman&ecirc; K&icirc;k&icirc; qala Evdal&ecirc; Zeynik&ecirc;
bike. Ev b&ucirc;yer&ecirc;n roman&ecirc; ji al&icirc; Ehmed&ecirc;
Ferman&ecirc; K&icirc;k&icirc; hatine gotin&ecirc;. Roman n&icirc;&#136;san
dide k&ucirc; &quot;edet&ecirc;n dengb&ecirc;j&icirc;y&ecirc;&quot;
gere bij&icirc;n. Ji bo v&ecirc; hewildanek heye. Ji dema Evdal&ecirc;
Zeynik&ecirc; heta b&ecirc; bigih&ecirc;je Ehmed&ecirc; Ferman&ecirc;
K&icirc;k&icirc;, &ccedil;i guhartin b&ucirc;ye &ucirc; van edetan
&ccedil;i tehr&ecirc;n n&ucirc; girtine?
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
L&ecirc; ez dixwazim ti&#136;stek&icirc; din b&ecirc;jim, di roman&ecirc;n
d&icirc;rok&icirc; de, dema k&ucirc; j&icirc;yana kes&ecirc;n
bi nav &ucirc; deng t&ecirc;n&ecirc; niv&icirc;sandin, gere meriv
van &#136;sexsan bi raste rast bide p&ecirc;&#136;s xwendewanan.
Z&ecirc;de an k&ecirc;m kirin neheq&icirc; ye.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Bi k&ecirc;fxwe&#136;sb&ucirc;n haya min b&ucirc; k&ucirc; Memet
&Ucirc;z&ucirc;n romaneka p&ecirc;ncem&icirc;n niv&icirc;s&icirc;ye,
y&ecirc; li Turk&icirc;y&ecirc; &ccedil;ap bibe. Naveroka roman&ecirc;,
j&icirc;yana Celadet Bedirxan e &ucirc; nav&ecirc; w&ecirc;, &quot;B&icirc;ra
Qeder&ecirc;&quot; ye. T&ecirc; zan&icirc;n k&ucirc; Celadet Beg
li S&ucirc;r&icirc;y&ecirc; b&icirc;reka av&ecirc; dida kolandin&ecirc;,
ew li cem b&icirc;re b&ucirc;, erd&ecirc; b&icirc;r&ecirc; k&ucirc;
hul&#136;s&icirc;ya, Celadet Beg bir&icirc;ndar b&ucirc; &ucirc;
&ccedil;&ucirc; ber rehma Xwed&ecirc;. Di v&ecirc; roman&ecirc;
de j&icirc;yana Celadet Beg&ecirc;, d&icirc;roka malbata Bedirxan&icirc;yan
&ucirc; daw&icirc;y&ecirc; de &ccedil;ilo ji d&icirc;rok&ecirc;
radibin, t&ecirc; p&ecirc;&#136;sber kirin.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Romana M e h m &ucirc; d B a k s &icirc; &quot;H&ecirc;l&icirc;n&quot;
li Stockholm&ecirc; 1984'an de &ccedil;ap b&ucirc;. Serp&ecirc;hat&icirc;ya
H&ecirc;l&icirc;n'&ecirc;, ya qehreman&ecirc; roman&ecirc;, bi
zimanek&icirc; xwe&#136;sik hat&icirc;ye niv&icirc;sandin. Ji
ber zordest&icirc;y&ecirc;, malbata H&ecirc;l&icirc;n'&ecirc;,
ji Turk&icirc;y&ecirc;, bi s&icirc;noran ve direvin di&ccedil;in
Lubnan'&ecirc; &ucirc; ji wir j&icirc; diherin Sw&ecirc;d'&ecirc;.
Roman bi k&ecirc;fa dil&ecirc; ciwan &ucirc; xortan e. Tirs, zehmet
&ucirc; xeter&ecirc;n li ser s&icirc;noran pirr ba&#136;s t&ecirc;
tesf&icirc;r kirin. Rohat, van be&#136;san &quot;edeb&icirc;yata
li ser s&icirc;noran&quot; qeb&ucirc;l dike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Romana Mehm&ucirc;d Baks&icirc;, ya duem&icirc;n, &quot;Gundik&ecirc;
Dono&quot; ye. Dora 1950'an, traktor &ucirc; motor k&ucirc; dikevin
gund&ecirc;n Xerzan, j&icirc;yan j&icirc; tev li hev dibe. &#136;Ser&ecirc;
gund&icirc; &ucirc; axan z&ecirc;de dibe. Di v&ecirc; roman&ecirc;
de ev mesel&ecirc;n n&ucirc;hat&icirc; t&ecirc;n p&ecirc;&#136;s
me. Rew&#136;sa jinan, ya zehmet &ucirc; zewaca wan a b&ecirc;dil
t&ecirc; li ser ziman. Mehm&ucirc;d ciwata kurd&icirc; ba&#136;s
nasdike.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
H e s e n &ecirc; M e t &ecirc; j&icirc; romana &quot;Lab&icirc;renta
Cinan&quot; niv&icirc;s&icirc;ye &ucirc; 1994'an de li Stockholm&ecirc;
&ccedil;ap b&ucirc;ye. Qehreman&ecirc; roman&ecirc; mamoste Kevanot
e &ucirc; roman li serp&ecirc;hat&icirc;ya w&icirc; hat&icirc;ye
avakirin. Ev mamostey&ecirc; &icirc;deal&icirc;st t&ecirc; li
dibistana, gundek&icirc; de kar dike &ucirc; demek&ecirc; &#136;s&ucirc;n
de d&icirc;n dibe, t&ecirc; li ser r&icirc;ya gund&icirc;yan.
Qil &ucirc; qal&ecirc;n gund&icirc;yan, ay&icirc;n &ucirc; b&ucirc;yer&ecirc;n
m&icirc;st&icirc;k h&ecirc;d&icirc; h&ecirc;d&icirc; mamoste j&icirc;
wek wan dike. Ev romana sosyo- ps&icirc;kolj&icirc;k num&ucirc;neyeka
p&ecirc;&#136;s&icirc;n e, pirsegir&ecirc;k&ecirc;n Kurd&icirc;,
y&ecirc;n civak&icirc; &ucirc; ps&icirc;koloj&icirc;k t&ecirc;n
ser ziman. Meriv k&ucirc; roman&ecirc; dixw&icirc;ne anal&icirc;z&ecirc;n
Gogol, &Ccedil;ehov &ucirc; Dostoyewsk&icirc; t&ecirc;n b&icirc;ra
mer&icirc;ya.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&#136;S a h &icirc; n &ecirc; S o r e k l &icirc; esl&ecirc; xwe
ve ji S&icirc;wereg'&ecirc; ye, li S&ucirc;r&icirc;y&ecirc; c&icirc;
b&ucirc;ye &ucirc; ana j&icirc; li Aw&ucirc;stralyay&ecirc; dij&icirc;,
romanek bi nav&ecirc; &quot;Wundab&ucirc;n&quot; niv&icirc;s&icirc;ye.
Di roman&ecirc; de dij&icirc; &quot;nezan&icirc;n&quot;&ecirc;
disekine. Ji bo serketin&ecirc; zaneb&ucirc;n lazim e. &quot;S&ucirc;c&ecirc;
k&ecirc;mas&icirc; &ucirc; b&ecirc;&ccedil;areb&ucirc;na y&ecirc;
bindest&quot; derdixe p&ecirc;&#136;s. Di v&icirc; war&icirc;
de carcaran ji heywanan m&icirc;nak dide.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
M e d e n &icirc; F e r h o j&icirc; di van n&ecirc;z&icirc;k&icirc;yan,
daw&icirc;ya sala 1994'an de romana xwe &quot;Berxwedan J&icirc;yane&quot;
&ccedil;ap kir. Min bi xwe hela h&ecirc; roman nexwend, ji ber
k&ucirc; min li Sw&ecirc;d&ecirc; destnexist.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
N a c &icirc; K u t l a y 1988'an de li Stockholm&ecirc; bi navek&icirc;
anon&icirc;m -N&ucirc;r&icirc; &#136;Semd&icirc;n- romana &quot;Zev&icirc;y&ecirc;n
Soro&quot; p&ecirc;&#136;sk&ecirc;&#136;s&icirc; xwendewanan kir.
Derdora 1950 de, dema k&ucirc; mak&icirc;ne &ucirc; traktor n&ucirc;
dikev&icirc;n li gund&ecirc;n Kurdan, &#136;ser&ecirc; axa &ucirc;
gund&icirc;yan, li ser erd&ecirc; her p&ecirc;&#136;s de di&ccedil;e.
Li gund&ecirc; Tend&ucirc;rek'&ecirc; de ber&ecirc; Ermen&icirc;
j&icirc; heb&ucirc;n. Di &#136;Ser&ecirc; Yekem&icirc;n &icirc;
Dinyay&ecirc; de ew hatin ku&#136;stin &ucirc; sirg&ucirc;n kirin.
Erd&ecirc;n wan j&icirc; ket dest&ecirc; axay&ecirc;n Kurdan.
Romaneka axa,gund&icirc;, zordest&icirc; &ucirc; bert&icirc;l
xwarina r&ecirc;vabir &ucirc; mem&ucirc;ran t&ecirc; n&icirc;&#136;sandan&ecirc;.
Ab&ucirc;qat&ecirc;n dur&ucirc;, bajarvan&icirc;y&ecirc;n k&ucirc;
gund&icirc;yan dixap&icirc;nin hene di roman&ecirc; de, l&ecirc;
hi&#136;syarb&ucirc;na gund&icirc;yan &ucirc; Fata Jineb&icirc;
j&icirc; heye. Roman&ecirc; gere di demeka din de dom bikira,
min ev pirs da xwendewanan k&ucirc; w&ecirc; j&icirc; binv&icirc;sim,
l&ecirc; hela h&ecirc;j&icirc; min pirsa xwe nehan&icirc; c&icirc;.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Derheq&ecirc; hinek roman niv&icirc;skar &ucirc; roman&ecirc;n
wan de dibe k&ucirc; min &ccedil;end nav b&icirc;rkirin. L&ecirc;
y&ecirc;n k&ucirc; ez dizanim evb&ucirc;n.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Di nav me Kurdan de neb&ucirc;ye edet k&ucirc; em li ser romanan
d&icirc;tin&ecirc;n xwe &ucirc; kr&icirc;t&icirc;k&ecirc;n &icirc;lm&icirc;
biniv&icirc;sin. Rohat di v&icirc; war&icirc; de hewil dide xwe
k&ucirc; v&ecirc; b&ecirc;deng&icirc;y&ecirc; bi&#136;sik&ecirc;ne.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
&copy; Nac&icirc; Kutlay
</BLOCKQUOTE>
