<HTML>
<HEAD>
<META HTTP-EQUIV="Content-Type" CONTENT="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1">
<TITLE>C:\NETSCAPE\NEWS\HR96-1.ASC</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.03z">
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../Images/Bakrund2.jpg" LINK="#0000ff" VLINK="#ff00ff">
<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=6 COLOR=#FFFF00>Human Rights Association
(IHD) of Turkey:</FONT></B></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=5 COLOR=#FFFF00>Balance for January, February
and March 1996<BR>
</FONT></B></CENTER>
<P>
<TABLE BORDER="1" CELLSPACING="18">
<TR><TD WIDTH=328><B><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR=#FFFF00>&quot;Shoot-to-kill&quot;(dubbed execution without trial) and death under custody</FONT></B>
</TD><TD WIDTH=328><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR=#FFFF00>39</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD WIDTH=328><B><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR=#FFFF00>Wounded in police raids</FONT></B>
</TD><TD WIDTH=328><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR=#FFFF00>30</FONT></TD></TR>
