<h1>Welcome to the Centre</h1>
<h3>Here we give you a premiere look from the new centre located at Laskou 
Street 10 A in the city of Rhodes.</h3>
<p><img src="images/bygget01.JPG" align=left hspace=10 width=250 height=189><em><strong>This is one of the guest-rooms for visiting writers 
and translators. The rooms are light with a high 
standard. Out of the window there is a lovely wiew 
over the Mediteranian Sea towards the shore of 
Turkey.</strong></em></p>
